#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New &gt;</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Novo &gt;</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you can choose to create one of four new items, as follows:"
msgstr "Tukaj lahko ustvarite enega od štirih novih elementov, kot sledi:"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>New Message...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Novo</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Novo sporočilo ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Compose a new message. This will open a Composer window, where you can write "
"a new message."
msgstr ""
"Sestavite novo sporočilo. To bo odprlo okno Skladatelj, kjer lahko napišete "
"novo sporočilo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Message from "
"Template &gt;</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Novo</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Sporočilo iz predloge &gt;</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates a new message from a selected template. Please see <link linkend="
"\"new-compose-from-templates\">Compose From Templates</link> for additional "
"information on creating templates. If you do not have any templates saved, "
"you will see <menuchoice> <guimenu>Message</guimenu><guisubmenu>Message from "
"Template &gt;</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>(no templates)</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Ustvari novo sporočilo iz izbrane predloge. Za dodatne informacije o "
"ustvarjanju predlog glejte <link linkend=\"new-compose-from-templates"
"\">Sestavi iz predlog</link>. Če nimate shranjenih predlog, boste videli "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guisubmenu>Sporočilo iz predloge "
"&gt;</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>(brez predlog)</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Add Folder..."
"</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Novo</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Dodaj "
"mapo ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates a new folder. The ensuing dialog will ask you to give the new folder "
"a name. The new folder will be created as a subfolder of the currently "
"selected folder."
msgstr ""
"Ustvari novo mapo. Pogovorno okno, ki sledi, vas bo pozvalo, da novi mapi "
"daste ime. Nova mapa bo ustvarjena kot podmapa trenutno izbrane mape."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>New "
"AddressBook Contact...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Novo</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Nov "
"stik v imeniku ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Launches the <ulink url=\"help:/kaddressbook/how-to-add-a-new-contact.html"
"\">New Contact</ulink> dialog, permitting you to add a new entry in "
"&kaddressbook;."
msgstr ""
"Zažene pogovorno okno <ulink url=\"help:/kaddressbook/how-to-add-a-new-"
"contact.html\">Nov stik</ulink>, ki vam omogoča dodajanje novega vnosa v "
"&kaddressbook;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Open...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>O</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Odpri ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens saved email messages (.mbox files)."
msgstr "Odpre shranjena e-poštna sporočila (datoteke .mbox)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Open Recent</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Odpri nedavno</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays a list of recently opened messages. Only those messages that have "
"been saved as .mbox files and subsequently opened will appear on this list. "
"If no such files exist, this menu item will be grayed out."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže seznam nedavno odprtih sporočil. Na tem seznamu bodo prikazana samo "
"tista sporočila, ki so bila shranjena kot datoteke .mbox in pozneje odprta. "
"Če takih datotek ni, bo ta element menija zatemnjen."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save As...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani kot ...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Saves the currently displayed message to a <filename role=\"extension\">."
"mbox</filename> file. This file includes all the headers and attachments, in "
"&MIME; format. If you want to save it as a different format (&eg;, as a "
"<filename role=\"extension\">.txt</filename> file), uncheck the "
"<guilabel>Automatically select filename extension (.mbox)</guilabel> box, "
"and add the filename extension before saving the file."
msgstr ""
"Shrani trenutno prikazano sporočilo v datoteko <filename role=\"extension\">."
"mbox</filename>. Ta datoteka vključuje vse glave in priloge v &MIME; format. "
"Če jo želite shraniti v drugi obliki (&eg; kot datoteko <filename role="
"\"extension\">.txt</filename>), počistite polje <guilabel>Samodejno izberi "
"pripono imena datoteke (.mbox)</guilabel> in dodajte pripono imena datoteke, "
"preden shranite datoteko."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Export to PDF...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izvozi v PDF ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exports the currently displayed message as a .pdf file."
msgstr "Izvozi trenutno prikazano sporočilo kot datoteko .pdf."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Import Messages...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Uvozi sporočila ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Starts up the <application>PIM Import Tool</application> program. This "
"application lets you import messages from several email clients into &kmail;."
msgstr ""
"Zažene program <application>Orodje za uvoz PIM</application>. Ta aplikacija "
"vam omogoča uvoz sporočil iz več e-poštnih odjemalcev v &kmail;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Print Preview...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Predogled tiskanja ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: menus.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shows how your email will appear when printed."
msgstr "Prikazuje, kako bo vaše e-poštno sporočilo prikazano ob tiskanju."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will only be enabled if a printer has been configured, is online, and "
"is available for use."
msgstr ""
"To bo omogočeno le, če je tiskalnik konfiguriran, je povezan in na voljo za "
"uporabo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Print...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Natisni ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays a dialog that lets you print the currently displayed message."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže pogovorno okno, v katerem lahko natisnete trenutno prikazano "
"sporočilo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Expire All Folders</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Poteče vse mape</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Deletes old messages from all folders. Deletion will occur according to the "
"rules in each folder's <link linkend=\"folders-properties-window"
"\">Properties dialog</link> (the default is not to delete old messages at "
"all)."
msgstr ""
"Izbriše stara sporočila iz vseh map. Izbris bo izveden v skladu s pravili v "
"<link linkend=\"folders-properties-window\">pogovornem oknu Lastnosti</link> "
"vsake mape (privzeto je, da se stara sporočila sploh ne izbrišejo)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Empty All Trash Folders</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izprazni vse mape koša</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this item to empty all trash folders, &ie;, the local trash folder and "
"all trash folders that may exist on &IMAP; servers. Messages in Trash will "
"be permanently deleted, and cannot be retrieved."
msgstr ""
"S tem elementom izpraznite vse mape s smetnjaki, &ie;, lokalno mapo s "
"smetnjaki in vse mape s smetnjaki, ki morda obstajajo na &IMAP; strežniki. "
"Sporočila v smetnjaku bodo trajno izbrisana in jih ni mogoče obnoviti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Work Offline</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Delo brez povezave</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets &kmail; to offline mode. This turns off all network jobs. This is "
"useful when working without a network connection. When selected, this item "
"will become <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Work Online</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, which must be selected to go back online "
"(required to send and receive email)."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi &kmail; v način brez povezave. To izklopi vsa omrežna opravila. To "
"je uporabno pri delu brez omrežne povezave. Ko je izbran, bo ta element "
"postal <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Delo na spletu</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, ki ga je treba izbrati, da se vrnete v splet "
"(potrebno za pošiljanje in prejemanje e-pošte)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Check Mail</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Preveri pošto</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid "Checks for new messages in all your accounts."
msgstr "Preveri nova sporočila v vseh vaših računih."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>Check Mail In &gt;</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Preverite pošto &gt;</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Checks for new messages from a particular account; your accounts will be "
"listed in a submenu."
msgstr ""
"Preverja nova sporočila iz določenega računa; vaši računi bodo navedeni v "
"podmeniju."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Send Queued Messages</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pošlji sporočila v čakalni vrsti</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sends the messages that are in your outbox. Messages can end up in your "
"outbox because of transmission errors, or because you composed and attempted "
"to send a message while offline. If there are no messages in your outbox, "
"this menu item will be grayed out."
msgstr ""
"Pošlje sporočila, ki so v pošiljanju. Sporočila se lahko znajdejo v mapi "
"»Odpošiljanje« zaradi napak pri prenosu ali ker ste sestavili in poskusili "
"poslati sporočilo brez povezave. Če v mapi za odpošiljanje ni sporočil, bo "
"ta element menija zatemnjen."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Send Queued Messages Via &gt;</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pošlji sporočila v čakalni vrsti "
"prek &gt;</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sends the messages that are in your outbox via a specific outgoing account. "
"This allows you to choose which server to use to send your queued messages. "
"Servers must be configured in the Configure &kmail; dialog, under the "
"<menuchoice><guiicon>Accounts</guiicon><guilabel>Sending</guilabel> </"
"menuchoice> tab, to be listed here. If there are no messages in the outbox "
"folder, this menu item will be grayed out."
msgstr ""
"Pošlje sporočila, ki so v vaši mapi za pošiljanje, prek določenega odhodnega "
"računa. To vam omogoča, da izberete, kateri strežnik želite uporabiti za "
"pošiljanje sporočil v čakalni vrsti. Strežniki morajo biti konfigurirani v "
"meniju Konfiguriraj &kmail; pod zavihkom <menuchoice><guiicon>Računi</"
"guiicon><guilabel>Pošiljanje</guilabel> </menuchoice>, ki bodo navedeni "
"tukaj. Če v mapi za odpošiljanje ni sporočil, bo ta element menija zatemnjen."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Delayed Messages...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zakasnjena sporočila ...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Starts the <ulink url=\"help:/akonadi_sendlater_agent\">Akonadi Send Later "
"Agent</ulink> dialog. Any messages queued for later delivery by the "
"composer's <menuchoice> <guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Send Later</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> option will appear in this dialog box. You can "
"modify and / or delete them. Note that delayed messages are stored in the "
"drafts folder, not in the outbox folder."
msgstr ""
"Zažene pogovorno okno <ulink url=\"help:/akonadi_sendlater_agent\">Posrednik "
"za kasnejše pošiljanje Akonadi</ulink>. V tem pogovornem oknu bodo prikazana "
"vsa sporočila, ki jih skladateljeva možnost <menuchoice> <guimenu>Sporočilo</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Pošlji pozneje</guimenuitem></menuchoice> postavi v "
"čakalno vrsto za kasnejšo dostavo. Lahko jih spremenite in/ali izbrišete. "
"Upoštevajte, da so zakasnjena sporočila shranjena v mapi z osnutki in ne v "
"mapi za pošiljanje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Followup Reminder Messages...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Sporočila o nadaljnjih opomnikih ..."
"</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Starts the <ulink url=\"help:/akonadi_followupreminder_agent\">Akonadi "
"Followup Reminder Agent</ulink> dialog. Any followup reminder messages "
"(\"todos\") created via the composer's <menuchoice> <guimenu>Options</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Create Followup Reminder...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"function will appear in this dialog box. You can delete those messages with "
"the &RMB; context menu."
msgstr ""
"Zažene pogovorno okno <ulink url=\"help:/akonadi_followupreminder_agent"
"\">Agent za nadaljnje opomnike Akonadi</ulink>. V tem pogovornem oknu bodo "
"prikazana vsa sporočila z opomniki o nadaljnjih dogodkih (»todos«), "
"ustvarjena prek skladateljeve funkcije <menuchoice> <guimenu>Možnosti</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Ustvari opomnik za nadaljnje ...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. Ta sporočila lahko izbrišete z &RMB; kontekstni meni."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exits &kmail;."
msgstr "Zapusti &kmail;."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:230 menus.docbook:1485
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edit Menu"
msgstr "Meni Uredi"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: menus.docbook:232 menus.docbook:1487
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Edit Menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Meni Urejanje</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: menus.docbook:238 menus.docbook:1493
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Edit Menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Meni Urejanje</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:241 menus.docbook:1496
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>The Edit Menu</para>"
msgstr "<para>Meni Urejanje</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the menu item you are looking for is missing, please see <ulink url="
"\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-edit\">Edit Menu</ulink> in &kde; "
"Fundamentals. The items listed here are &kmail; specific."
msgstr ""
"Če element menija, ki ga iščete, manjka, glejte <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/menus.html#menus-edit\">Meni Uredi</ulink> v &kde; Osnove. "
"Tukaj navedeni elementi so &kmail; specifična."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>C</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Copy Folder</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>C</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Kopiraj mapo</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates an \"Akonadi\" pointer to the entire contents of the currently "
"selected folder, and copies that pointer to the clipboard. A subsequent "
"paste operation in a text editor will simply paste the pointer text. A "
"subsequent paste operation in a &kmail; folder (or in the &dolphin; file "
"manager) will create a second copy of the folder and its contents."
msgstr ""
"Ustvari kazalec »Akonadi« na celotno vsebino trenutno izbrane mape in kopira "
"ta kazalec v odložišče. Naslednja operacija lepljenja v urejevalniku "
"besedila bo preprosto prilepila besedilo kazalca. Naknadna operacija "
"lepljenja v &kmail; (ali v upravitelju datotek &dolphin;) bo ustvaril drugo "
"kopijo mape in njene vsebine."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Cut Folder</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izreži mapo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates an \"Akonadi\" pointer to the currently selected folder, and copies "
"that pointer to the clipboard. A subsequent \"paste\" operation in a text "
"editor or in &dolphin; will behave exactly like the preceding "
"<guimenuitem>Copy Folder</guimenuitem> operation. A subsequent paste "
"operation in &kmail; will move the folder and its contents to a different "
"location (if pasted in some folder other than the originating folder)."
msgstr ""
"Ustvari kazalec »Akonadi« na trenutno izbrano mapo in kopira ta kazalec v "
"odložišče. Naknadna operacija \"prilepi\" v urejevalniku besedil ali v "
"&dolphin; se bo obnašal natanko tako kot prejšnja operacija "
"<guimenuitem>Kopiraj mapo</guimenuitem>. Naknadna operacija lepljenja v "
"&kmail; premakne mapo in njeno vsebino na drugo lokacijo (če je prilepljena "
"v drugo mapo, ki ni izvorna mapa)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>C</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Copy Message</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>C</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Kopiraj sporočilo</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates an \"Akonadi\" pointer to the currently selected message(s), and "
"copies that pointer to the clipboard. A subsequent paste operation in a text "
"editor will simply paste the pointer text. A subsequent paste operation in a "
"&kmail; folder (or in the &dolphin; file manager) will create a copy of the "
"message(s), headers and all."
msgstr ""
"Ustvari kazalec »Akonadi« na trenutno izbrana sporočila in kopira ta kazalec "
"v odložišče. Naslednja operacija lepljenja v urejevalniku besedila bo "
"preprosto prilepila besedilo kazalca. Naknadna operacija lepljenja v &kmail; "
"(ali v upravitelju datotek &dolphin;) bo ustvaril kopijo sporočil(a), glav "
"in vsega."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>X</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Cut Message</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>X</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izreži sporočilo</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates an \"Akonadi\" pointer to the currently selected message(s), and "
"copies that pointer to the clipboard. A subsequent \"paste\" operation in a "
"text editor or in &dolphin; will behave exactly like the preceding "
"<guimenuitem>Copy Message</guimenuitem> operation. A subsequent paste "
"operation in &kmail; will either create a second copy of the message(s) (if "
"pasted in the originating folder) or move the message(s) to a different "
"folder (if pasted in some folder other than the originating folder)."
msgstr ""
"Ustvari kazalec »Akonadi« na trenutno izbrana sporočila in kopira ta kazalec "
"v odložišče. Naknadna operacija \"prilepi\" v urejevalniku besedil ali v "
"&dolphin; se bo obnašal natanko tako kot prejšnja operacija "
"<guimenuitem>Kopiraj sporočilo</guimenuitem>. Naknadna operacija lepljenja v "
"&kmail; bodisi ustvari drugo kopijo sporočil(a) (če je prilepljeno v izvorno "
"mapo) ali premakne sporočilo(a) v drugo mapo (če je prilepljeno v drugo mapo "
"kot izvorna mapa)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut>&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut>&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Prilepi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pastes either the entire contents of a folder, or the contents of selected "
"messages, depending on the operation that preceded the \"paste\". This "
"operation cannot be used to paste selected text inside the reader window. If "
"no copy / cut operation is pending, this option will be grayed out."
msgstr ""
"Prilepi celotno vsebino mape ali vsebino izbranih sporočil, odvisno od "
"operacije, ki je bila izvedena pred \"prilepi\". Te operacije ni mogoče "
"uporabiti za lepljenje izbranega besedila v okno bralnika. Če ni na čakanju "
"nobena operacija kopiranja/izrezovanja, bo ta možnost zatemnjena."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut>&Del;</shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Move to "
"Trash</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut>&Del;</shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Premakni v "
"koš</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Moves the selected messages to the trash folder. If the selected messages "
"are already in the trash folder, they will be permanently deleted."
msgstr ""
"Premakne izbrana sporočila v mapo smeti. Če so izbrana sporočila že v "
"smetnjaku, bodo trajno izbrisana."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:307
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Del;</keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Move Thread to Trash</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Del;</keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Premakni nit v koš</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Moves the selected thread to the trash folder, &eg;, a conversation in a "
"mailing list."
msgstr "Premakne izbrano nit v mapo smeti, &eg; pogovor na poštnem seznamu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Find in Message...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Najdi v sporočilu ...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Searches the current message text for a string entered in the <guilabel>Find:"
"</guilabel> textbox."
msgstr ""
"V trenutnem besedilu sporočila poišče niz, ki je vnesen v besedilno polje "
"<guilabel>Najdi:</guilabel>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Select All Messages</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izberi vsa sporočila</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selects all messages in the current folder."
msgstr "Izbere vsa sporočila v trenutni mapi."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Select All Text</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>T</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izberi vse besedilo</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selects the text of the currently displayed message."
msgstr "Označi besedilo trenutno prikazanega sporočila."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:337 menus.docbook:1619
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Menu"
msgstr "Meni Pogled"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: menus.docbook:339 menus.docbook:1621
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The View Menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Meni Pogled</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: menus.docbook:345 menus.docbook:1627
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The View Menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Meni Pogled</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:348 menus.docbook:1630
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>The View Menu</para>"
msgstr "<para>Meni Pogled</para>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Message List &gt;</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Ogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Seznam sporočil &gt;</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This submenu has the following options to change the appearance of the "
"message list."
msgstr ""
"Ta podmeni ima naslednje možnosti za spreminjanje videza seznama sporočil."

#. Tag: guisubmenu
#: menus.docbook:361
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sorting &gt;"
msgstr "Razvrščanje &gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "Contains options to customize your sort order as follows:"
msgstr "Vsebuje možnosti za prilagajanje vrstnega reda na naslednji način:"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Message Sort Order</guilabel> has several options, most of which "
"are self-explanatory. The following options may not be immediately obvious, "
"and deserve an explanation."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Vrstni red razvrščanja sporočil</guilabel> ima več možnosti, ki so "
"večinoma razumljive same po sebi. Naslednje možnosti morda niso takoj očitne "
"in si zaslužijo razlago."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>By Smart Sender/Receiver</guilabel> will display the receiver when "
"you are viewing the sent-mail folder, and will display the sender when you "
"are viewing the inbox."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>S pametnim pošiljateljem/prejemnikom</guilabel> bo prikazal "
"prejemnika, ko si ogledujete mapo s poslano pošto, in bo prikazal "
"pošiljatelja, ko si ogledujete mapo »Prejeto«."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>By Action Item Status</guilabel> and <guilabel>By Important "
"Status</guilabel>. These flags need to be set before they can be sorted. "
"Please see <link linkend=\"reader-mark-messages\">Mark Messages</link> for "
"more information on marking your messages."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Po stanju elementa dejanja</guilabel> in <guilabel>Po pomembnem "
"stanju</guilabel>. Te zastavice je treba nastaviti, preden jih je mogoče "
"razvrstiti. Za več informacij o označevanju sporočil glejte <link linkend="
"\"reader-mark-messages\">Označi sporočila</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Message Sort Direction</guilabel> and <guilabel>Group Sort "
"Direction</guilabel> allow you to change the direction in which your "
"messages/groups will be sorted, respectively. Note that the \"Group\" "
"options are only available when messages are aggregated into groups."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Smer razvrščanja sporočil</guilabel> in <guilabel>Smer razvrščanja "
"skupin</guilabel> vam omogočata, da spremenite smer, v kateri bodo "
"razvrščena vaša sporočila/skupine. Upoštevajte, da so možnosti »Skupina« na "
"voljo le, ko so sporočila združena v skupine."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Folder always Uses this Sort Order</guilabel> allows you to "
"specify different sort settings for each folder."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Mapa vedno uporablja ta vrstni red</guilabel> vam omogoča, da "
"določite različne nastavitve razvrščanja za vsako mapo."

#. Tag: guisubmenu
#: menus.docbook:386
#, no-c-format
msgid "Aggregation &gt;"
msgstr "Združevanje &gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lets you select an aggregation option. Please see the <link linkend="
"\"configure-appearance-message-list\">Message List Appearance</link> tab "
"(under <menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure "
"&kmail;...</guisubmenu></menuchoice>) for more information on aggregation."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča izbiro možnosti združevanja. Oglejte si zavihek <link linkend="
"\"configure-appearance-message-list\">Videz seznama sporočil</link> (pod "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj &kmail;..."
"</guisubmenu ></menuchoice>) za več informacij o združevanju."

#. Tag: guisubmenu
#: menus.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid "Theme &gt;"
msgstr "Tema &gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:395
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lets you select a theme. Please see the <link linkend=\"configure-appearance-"
"message-list\">Message List Appearance</link> tab (under <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure &kmail;...</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice>) for more information on themes."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča izbiro teme. Oglejte si zavihek <link linkend=\"configure-appearance-"
"message-list\">Videz seznama sporočil</link> (pod <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Konfiguriraj &kmail;...</guisubmenu "
"></menuchoice>) za več informacij o temah."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>O</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guisubmenu>Create New Tab</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>O</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guisubmenu>Ustvari nov zavihek</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:404
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates a new tab on the tabbing toolbar. This tab will point to the folder "
"you are viewing when the option is selected. If the tabbing toolbar is not "
"yet visible, selecting this option will create it. The tabbing toolbar can "
"be handy if you have many folders, but only a few of them are regularly "
"accessed."
msgstr ""
"Ustvari nov zavihek v orodni vrstici z zavihki. Ta zavihek bo pokazal na "
"mapo, ki si jo ogledujete, ko je izbrana možnost. Če orodna vrstica z "
"zavihki še ni vidna, jo boste ustvarili z izbiro te možnosti. Orodna vrstica "
"z zavihki je lahko priročna, če imate veliko map, vendar redno dostopate le "
"do nekaterih."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:411
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&PgDn;</keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guisubmenu>Activate Next Tab</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&PgDn;</keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guisubmenu>Aktiviraj naslednji zavihek</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:413
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens the folder associated with the next tab on the tabbing toolbar."
msgstr "Odpre mapo, povezano z naslednjim zavihkom v orodni vrstici z zavihki."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:417
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&PgUp;</keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guisubmenu>Activate Previous Tab</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&PgUp;</keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guisubmenu>Aktiviraj prejšnji zavihek</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:419
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the folder associated with the previous tab on the tabbing toolbar."
msgstr "Odpre mapo, povezano s prejšnjim zavihkom v orodni vrstici z zavihki."

#. Tag: guisubmenu
#: menus.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move Tab Left"
msgstr "Premakni zavihek levo"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:424
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Reorders the tabs on the tabbing toolbar by shifting the active tab to the "
"left. If that tab is already at the extreme left end, it will be moved to "
"the right hand end position."
msgstr ""
"Prerazporedi zavihke v orodni vrstici z zavihki tako, da premakne aktivni "
"zavihek v levo. Če je ta zavihek že na skrajnem levem koncu, bo premaknjen "
"na desni končni položaj."

#. Tag: guisubmenu
#: menus.docbook:429
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move Tab Right"
msgstr "Premakni zavihek desno"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:430
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Reorders the tabs on the tabbing toolbar by shifting the active tab to the "
"right. If that tab is already at the extreme right end, it will be moved to "
"the left hand end position."
msgstr ""
"Prerazporedi zavihke v orodni vrstici z zavihki tako, da premakne aktivni "
"zavihek v desno. Če je ta jeziček že na skrajnem desnem koncu, bo premaknjen "
"na levi končni položaj."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:435
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>W</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guisubmenu>Close Tab</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>W</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guisubmenu>Zapri zavihek</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: action
#: menus.docbook:437
#, no-c-format
msgid "Closes the currently selected tab."
msgstr "Zapre trenutno izbrani zavihek."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:445
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Headers &gt;</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Glave &gt;</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:446
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selects your headers view. Please see <link linkend=\"using-header-options"
"\">Header Options</link> for details on the available header views."
msgstr ""
"Izbere pogled vaših glav. Oglejte si <link linkend=\"using-header-options"
"\">Možnosti glave</link> za podrobnosti o razpoložljivih pogledih glave."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Attachments &gt;</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Priponke &gt;</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:452
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Changes the way attachments appear in the <guilabel>Message Preview Pane</"
"guilabel> (independent of the &MIME; Tree). Please see <link linkend=\"using-"
"attachment-view-options\">Attachment Options</link> for details on viewing "
"attachments."
msgstr ""
"Spremeni način, kako so priloge prikazane v <guilabel>Podoknu za predogled "
"sporočil</guilabel> (neodvisno od drevesa &MIME;). Za podrobnosti o ogledu "
"prilog glejte <link linkend=\"using-attachment-view-options\">Možnosti "
"priloge</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>.</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>View</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Expand Thread / Group</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>.</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Razširi nit / skupino</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:460
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will display the thread of the current message, &ie;, all messages that "
"are replies to the current message."
msgstr ""
"To bo prikazalo nit trenutnega sporočila, &ie;, vsa sporočila, ki so "
"odgovori na trenutno sporočilo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>,</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>View</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Collapse Thread / Group</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>,</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Strni nit/skupino</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:467
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will hide the thread of the current message, &ie;, it will hide all "
"messages that are replies to the current message."
msgstr ""
"To bo skrilo nit trenutnega sporočila, &ie;, skrila bo vsa sporočila, ki so "
"odgovori na trenutno sporočilo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:472
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>.</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Expand All Threads</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>.</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Razširi vse niti</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:474
#, no-c-format
msgid "Expands all threads in the current folder."
msgstr "Razširi vse niti v trenutni mapi."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:478
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>,</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Collapse All Threads</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>,</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Strni vse niti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid "Collapses all threads in the current folder."
msgstr "Strni vse niti v trenutni mapi."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:484
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save Display Format</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani obliko prikaza</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:485
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option is apparently supposed to save something somewhere, but it's not "
"yet working correctly."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost naj bi očitno nekam nekaj shranila, vendar še ne deluje pravilno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:490
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Restore Display Format</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Obnovi obliko prikaza</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option is apparently supposed to restore whatever the preceding \"Save"
"\" option is supposed to save, but it's not yet working correctly, either."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost naj bi očitno obnovila vse, kar naj bi prejšnja možnost »Shrani« "
"shranila, vendar tudi ta še ne deluje pravilno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Disable Emoticon</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Onemogoči emotikon</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to stop &kmail; from transforming <literal>:-)</literal> "
"into <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"smile.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, da ustavite &kmail; iz preoblikovanja <literal>:-)</"
"literal> v <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"smile.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>X</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>View</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Use Fixed Font</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>X</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Uporabi fiksno pisavo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:505
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Uses a fixed width (Monospace) font to display the messages in the current "
"folder. The font to be used can be configured in the <link linkend="
"\"configure-appearance-fonts\">Fonts</link> tab on the <guilabel>Appearance</"
"guilabel> page of the &kmail; configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"Za prikaz sporočil v trenutni mapi uporablja pisavo s fiksno širino "
"(enoprostor). Uporabljeno pisavo lahko konfigurirate v zavihku <link linkend="
"\"configure-appearance-fonts\">Pisave</link> na strani <guilabel>Videz</"
"guilabel> aplikacije &kmail; konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:511
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Set Encoding &gt;</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Nastavite kodiranje &gt;</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lets you choose the character encoding to be used in the Message Pane. The "
"default, <guilabel>Auto</guilabel>, should work in almost every case."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča izbiro kodiranja znakov, ki bo uporabljeno v podoknu za sporočila. "
"Privzeta nastavitev, <guilabel>Samodejno</guilabel>, bi morala delovati v "
"skoraj vseh primerih."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:517
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Zoom &gt;</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Povečaj &gt;</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:518
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option lets you zoom in or out on every message displayed in the "
"preview pane."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost vam omogoča, da povečate ali pomanjšate vsako sporočilo, "
"prikazano v podoknu za predogled."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:528
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go Menu"
msgstr "Pojdi meni"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: menus.docbook:530
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Go Menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Meni Pojdi</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: menus.docbook:536
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Go Menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Meni Pojdi</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:539
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>The Go Menu</para>"
msgstr "<para>Meni Pojdi</para>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:547
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>J</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Go</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Jump to Folder...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>J</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Pojdi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Skoči v mapo ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:549
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows a dialog box with a list of all your folders. Click on the folder you "
"wish to view, and that folder will be opened for display in the message "
"preview pane."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže pogovorno okno s seznamom vseh vaših map. Kliknite mapo, ki si jo "
"želite ogledati, in ta mapa se bo odprla za prikaz v podoknu za predogled "
"sporočila."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:554
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>N</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Go</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Next Message</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>N</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Pojdi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Naslednje sporočilo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:556
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selects the next message in the message list. The keyboard shortcut &Right; "
"also performs this function."
msgstr ""
"Izbere naslednje sporočilo na seznamu sporočil. Bližnjica na tipkovnici "
"&Right; opravlja tudi to funkcijo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:561
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>&plus;</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Go</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Next Unread Message</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>&plus;</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Pojdi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Naslednje neprebrano sporočilo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:563
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selects the next unread message in the message list. If there are no unread "
"messages below the currently selected message, the behavior depends on the "
"value of the <xref linkend=\"configure-misc-folders-go-unread\"/> option."
msgstr ""
"Izbere naslednje neprebrano sporočilo na seznamu sporočil. Če pod trenutno "
"izbranim sporočilom ni neprebranih sporočil, je vedenje odvisno od vrednosti "
"možnosti <xref linkend=\"configure-misc-folders-go-unread\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:569
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>P</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Go</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Previous Message</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>P</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Pojdi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Prejšnje sporočilo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:571
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selects the previous message in the message list."
msgstr "Izbere prejšnje sporočilo na seznamu sporočil."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:575
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>&minus;</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Go</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Previous Unread Message</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>&minus;</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Pojdi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Prejšnje neprebrano sporočilo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:577
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selects the previous unread message in the message list. If there is no "
"unread message above the currently selected message, then the behavior "
"depends on the value of the <xref linkend=\"configure-misc-folders-go-unread"
"\"/> option."
msgstr ""
"Izbere prejšnje neprebrano sporočilo na seznamu sporočil. Če nad trenutno "
"izbranim sporočilom ni neprebranega sporočila, je vedenje odvisno od "
"vrednosti možnosti <xref linkend=\"configure-misc-folders-go-unread\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:583
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>&plus;</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu><guimenuitem>Next Unread Folder</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>&plus;</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Naslednja "
"neprebrana mapa</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:585
#, no-c-format
msgid "Jumps to the next folder with unread messages."
msgstr "Skoči na naslednjo mapo z neprebranimi sporočili."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:589
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>&minus;</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu><guimenuitem>Previous Unread "
"Folder</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>&minus;</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prejšnja "
"neprebrana mapa</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:591
#, no-c-format
msgid "Jumps to the previous folder with unread messages."
msgstr "Skoči na prejšnjo mapo z neprebranimi sporočili."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:595
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut>&Space;</shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu><guimenuitem>Next Unread "
"Text</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut>&Space;</shortcut> <guimenu>Pojdi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Naslednje "
"neprebrano besedilo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:597
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scrolls down if you are not yet at the bottom of a message, otherwise jumps "
"to the next unread message."
msgstr ""
"Pomakne se navzdol, če še niste na dnu sporočila, sicer skoči na naslednje "
"neprebrano sporočilo."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:606
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folder Menu"
msgstr "Meni mape"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: menus.docbook:608
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Folder Menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Meni mape</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: menus.docbook:614
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Folder Menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Meni mape</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:617
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>The Folder Menu</para>"
msgstr "<para>Meni mape</para>"

#. Tag: guimenu
#: menus.docbook:625
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folder Properties"
msgstr "Lastnosti mape"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:626
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the <link linkend=\"folders-properties-window\">Folder Properties</"
"link> dialog that lets you modify the properties of the current folder."
msgstr ""
"Odpre pogovorno okno <link linkend=\"folders-properties-window\">Lastnosti "
"mape</link>, ki vam omogoča spreminjanje lastnosti trenutne mape."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:631
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Folder</guimenu><guimenuitem>Add Folder...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Mapa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Dodaj mapo ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:632
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Prompts you for a name, then creates a new folder as a subfolder of the "
"current folder. This is exactly like <xref linkend=\"reader-add-folder\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Vpraša vas k imenu, nato pa ustvari novo mapo kot podmapo trenutne mape. To "
"je natanko tako kot <xref linkend=\"reader-add-folder\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:637
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Folder</guimenu><guimenuitem>Mark All Messages as Read</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Mapa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Označi vsa sporočila kot prebrana</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:638
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the status of all unread messages in the current folder to \"read\"."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi status vseh neprebranih sporočil v trenutni mapi na \"prebrano\"."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:642
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Folder</guimenu><guimenuitem>Mark All Messages as Read in This "
"Folder and All its Subfolders</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Mapa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Označi vsa sporočila kot prebrana v tej "
"mapi in vseh njenih podmapah</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:644
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the status of all unread messages in the current folder (and all its "
"subfolders) to \"read\"."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi status vseh neprebranih sporočil v trenutni mapi (in vseh njenih "
"podmapah) na \"prebrano\"."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:649
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Folder</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Update Folder</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Mapa</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Posodobi mapo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:651
#, no-c-format
msgid "Checks whether new mail has arrived in the currently selected folder."
msgstr "Preveri, ali je nova pošta prispela v trenutno izbrano mapo."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:652 menus.docbook:661
#, no-c-format
msgid "This option only works in &IMAP; folders."
msgstr "Ta možnost deluje samo v &IMAP; mape."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:657
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F5</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Folder</guimenu><guimenuitem>Update This Folder and All "
"Its Subfolders</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F5</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Mapa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Posodobi to mapo in vse njene "
"podmape</guimenuitem >"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:659
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Checks whether new mail has arrived in the currently selected folder, or in "
"any of its subfolders."
msgstr ""
"Preveri, ali je nova pošta prispela v trenutno izbrano mapo ali katero od "
"njenih podmap."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:666
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Folder</guimenu><guimenuitem>Move All Messages to Trash</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Mapa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Premakni vsa sporočila v koš</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:667
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moves all of the messages in the selected folder into the trash folder."
msgstr "Premakne vsa sporočila v izbrani mapi v mapo smeti."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:668
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is only available if the currently selected folder is not a trash "
"folder. If the currently selected folder is a trash folder, you will see "
"<guilabel>Empty Trash</guilabel>, instead. Selecting that option will empty "
"the trash by permanently deleting the messages in the trash folder."
msgstr ""
"To je na voljo le, če trenutno izbrana mapa ni mapa smetnjaka. Če je "
"trenutno izbrana mapa smetnjak, boste namesto tega videli <guilabel>Prazni "
"smetnjak</guilabel>. Če izberete to možnost, boste izpraznili koš tako, da "
"boste trajno izbrisali sporočila v mapi smetnjaka."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:675
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Folder</guimenu><guimenuitem>Delete Folder</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Mapa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izbriši mapo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:676
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Deletes the selected folder and all its contents. A warning message will be "
"displayed. If the current folder is one of &kmail;'s pre-defined folders "
"(inbox, &etc;), this menu item will be grayed out."
msgstr ""
"Izbriše izbrano mapo in vso njeno vsebino. Prikaže se opozorilno sporočilo. "
"Če je trenutna mapa ena od vnaprej določenih map &kmail; (prejeto &etc;), bo "
"ta menijska postavka zatemnjena."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:682
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Folder</guimenu><guimenuitem>Archive Folder...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Mapa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Arhivska mapa ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:683
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Brings up a dialog so you can create an archive of the currently selected "
"folder. Please see the <xref linkend=\"folder-archive\"/> section of \"Using "
"&kmail;\" for details."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže pogovorno okno, v katerem lahko ustvarite arhiv trenutno izbrane "
"mape. Oglejte si razdelek <xref linkend=\"folder-archive\"/> \"Uporaba "
"&kmail;\" za podrobnosti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:688
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>*</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Folder</guimenu><guimenuitem>Remove Duplicate Messages</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>*</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Mapa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Odstrani podvojena sporočila</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:690
#, no-c-format
msgid "Searches the folder for duplicate messages and deletes them."
msgstr "V mapi poišče podvojena sporočila in jih izbriše."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:694
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Folder</guimenu><guimenuitem>Remove Duplicates in This Folder and "
"All its Subfolder</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Mapa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Odstrani dvojnike v tej mapi in vseh "
"njenih podmapah</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:696
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Searches the folder, and its subfolders, for duplicate messages, then "
"deletes the duplicates."
msgstr ""
"V mapi in njenih podmapah poišče podvojena sporočila, nato pa jih izbriše."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:701
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Folder</guimenu><guimenuitem>Apply Filters On Folder &gt;</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Mapa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Uporabi filtre za mapo &gt;</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:702
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Applies selected filters (All, Spam, or Not Spam) to the currently selected "
"folder. Please see the <link linkend=\"filter-dialog-id\">Filter dialog</"
"link> for more information on filters."
msgstr ""
"Uporabi izbrane filtre (Vse, Neželena pošta ali Ne vsiljena pošta) za "
"trenutno izbrano mapo. Za več informacij o filtrih si oglejte <link linkend="
"\"filter-dialog-id\">pogovorno okno Filter</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:707
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Folder</guimenu><guimenuitem>Apply Filters On Folder and All its "
"Subfolders &gt;</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Mapa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Uporabi filtre za mapo in vse njene "
"podmape &gt;</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:709
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Applies selected filters (All, Spam, or Not Spam) to the currently selected "
"folder, and to its subfolders. Please see the <link linkend=\"filter-dialog-"
"id\">Filter dialog</link> for more information on filters."
msgstr ""
"Uporabi izbrane filtre (Vse, Neželena pošta ali Ne vsiljena pošta) za "
"trenutno izbrano mapo in njene podmape. Za več informacij o filtrih si "
"oglejte <link linkend=\"filter-dialog-id\">pogovorno okno Filter</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:714
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Folder</guimenu><guimenuitem>Message Default Format &gt;</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Mapa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Privzeta oblika sporočila &gt;</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:715
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you may select one of three options: <guilabel>Prefer &HTML; to Plain "
"Text</guilabel>, <guilabel>Prefer Plain Text to &HTML;</guilabel>, or "
"<guilabel>Use Global Setting</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko izberete eno od treh možnosti: <guilabel>Raje &HTML; pred golim "
"besedilom</guilabel>, <guilabel>Raje navadno besedilo pred &HTML;</guilabel> "
"ali <guilabel>Uporabi globalno nastavitev</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:717
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For security reasons, we recommend you only select <guilabel>Prefer &HTML; "
"to Plain Text</guilabel> in folders which can never contain untrusted "
"messages."
msgstr ""
"Iz varnostnih razlogov priporočamo, da izberete samo <guilabel>Raje &HTML; v "
"navadno besedilo</guilabel> v mapah, ki nikoli ne smejo vsebovati "
"nezaupljivih sporočil."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:723
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Folder</guimenu><guimenuitem>Load External References</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Mapa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Naloži zunanje reference</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:724
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have &HTML; messages enabled (see above), then you will also have the "
"option to have images and other resources linked from the web downloaded "
"automatically."
msgstr ""
"Če imate &HTML; sporočila omogočena (glejte zgoraj), potem boste imeli tudi "
"možnost, da se slike in drugi viri, povezani s spleta, samodejno prenesejo."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:726
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option is only available if <guilabel>Prefer &HTML; to Plain Text</"
"guilabel> has been selected. If you turn this option on, and later decide to "
"change <guimenuitem>Message Default Format</guimenuitem>, be sure to clear "
"this checkbox before making the switch. There is a bug in &kmail; -- if the "
"checkbox on this item has not been cleared, and this option has been grayed "
"out, results are unpredictable."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost je na voljo samo, če <guilabel>Raje &HTML; v golo besedilo</"
"guilabel>je bil izbran. Če vklopite to možnost in se pozneje odločite "
"spremeniti <guimenuitem>Privzeto obliko sporočila</guimenuitem>, pred "
"preklopom počistite to potrditveno polje. V &kmail; -- če potrditveno polje "
"pri tem elementu ni počiščeno in je ta možnost zatemnjena, so rezultati "
"nepredvidljivi."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:735
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Folder</guimenu><guimenuitem>Mailing List Management...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Mapa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Upravljanje poštnega seznama ...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:736
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This opens the mailing list management dialog. This option is only available "
"if the current folder contains messages from a mailing list. Please see the "
"<link linkend=\"folders-properties-mailinglist\">Mailing List dialog</link> "
"for more information on mailing lists."
msgstr ""
"To odpre pogovorno okno za upravljanje poštnega seznama. Ta možnost je na "
"voljo le, če trenutna mapa vsebuje sporočila z poštnega seznama. Za več "
"informacij o poštnih seznamih si oglejte <link linkend=\"folders-properties-"
"mailinglist\">pogovorno okno poštnih seznamov</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:743
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Folder</guimenu><guimenuitem>Assign Shortcut...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Mapa</guimenu><guimenuitem>Dodeli bližnjico ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:744
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This lets you assign a keyboard shortcut to the currently selected folder."
msgstr ""
"To vam omogoča, da trenutno izbrani mapi dodelite bližnjico na tipkovnici."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:752 menus.docbook:1356
#, no-c-format
msgid "Message Menu"
msgstr "Meni Sporočila"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: menus.docbook:754 menus.docbook:1358
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Message Menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Meni Sporočila</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: menus.docbook:760 menus.docbook:1364
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Message Menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Meni Sporočila</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:763 menus.docbook:1367
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>The Message Menu</para>"
msgstr "<para>Meni Sporočila</para>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:771
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>New Message...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Novo sporočilo ...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:773
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the <link linkend=\"the-composer-window\">composer window</link> so "
"you can write a new message."
msgstr ""
"Odpre <link linkend=\"the-composer-window\">okno skladatelja</link>, da "
"lahko napišete novo sporočilo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:778
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>N</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>New Message to "
"Mailing-List...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>N</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Novo sporočilo "
"na poštni seznam.. .</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:780
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the composer window so you can write a new message. If the current "
"folder holds a mailing list and has a posting address defined, that posting "
"address will automatically be entered as the <guilabel>To:</guilabel> "
"address when the composer window is opened. If the current folder does not "
"contain a mailing list, this item will be grayed out."
msgstr ""
"Odpre okno skladatelja, da lahko napišete novo sporočilo. Če trenutna mapa "
"vsebuje poštni seznam in ima določen naslov za objavo, bo ta naslov za "
"objavo samodejno vnesen kot naslov <guilabel>Za:</guilabel>, ko se odpre "
"okno za sestavljanje. Če trenutna mapa ne vsebuje poštnega seznama, bo ta "
"element zatemnjen."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:788
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>R</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Message</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Reply...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>R</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Sporočilo</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Odgovori ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:790
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the composer window, inserts quoted text from the currently selected "
"message, and sets the <guilabel>To:</guilabel> field to either the mailing-"
"list address (if you reply to a mailing-list message), or to the preferred "
"reply-to address of the sender. If you want to control which address is set "
"in the <guilabel>To:</guilabel> field, you should use <link linkend=\"reader-"
"message-reply-special\">Reply Special</link>. The sending identity will "
"automatically be set to the identity to which this message was addressed."
msgstr ""
"Odpre okno skladatelja, vstavi citirano besedilo iz trenutno izbranega "
"sporočila in nastavi polje <guilabel>Za:</guilabel> na naslov poštnega "
"seznama (če odgovarjate na sporočilo poštnega seznama) ali na želeno naslov "
"za odgovor pošiljatelja. Če želite nadzorovati, kateri naslov je nastavljen "
"v polju <guilabel>Za:</guilabel>, morate uporabiti <link linkend=\"reader-"
"message-reply-special\">Poseben odgovor</link>. Identiteta pošiljatelja bo "
"samodejno nastavljena na identiteto, na katero je bilo to sporočilo "
"naslovljeno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:798
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>A</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Message</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Reply to All...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>A</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Sporočilo</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Odgovori vsem ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:800
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the composer window, inserts the quoted text of the currently selected "
"message, and sets the <guilabel>To:</guilabel> field to either the mailing-"
"list address (when replying to a mailing-list message), or to the preferred "
"reply-to address of the sender. The <guilabel>Copy to (CC):</guilabel> field "
"is filled with the addresses of all the other recipients of the currently "
"selected message, excluding your own address. The sending identity will "
"automatically be set to the identity to which this message was addressed."
msgstr ""
"Odpre okno za sestavljanje, vstavi citirano besedilo trenutno izbranega "
"sporočila in nastavi polje <guilabel>Za:</guilabel> na naslov poštnega "
"seznama (ko odgovarjate na sporočilo poštnega seznama) ali na želeno naslov "
"za odgovor pošiljatelja. Polje <guilabel>Kopiraj v (CC):</guilabel> je "
"izpolnjeno z naslovi vseh drugih prejemnikov trenutno izbranega sporočila, "
"razen vašega naslova. Identiteta pošiljatelja bo samodejno nastavljena na "
"identiteto, na katero je bilo to sporočilo naslovljeno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:811
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Message</guimenu><guisubmenu>Reply Special &gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Reply to Author...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>A</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guisubmenu>Posebni odgovor &gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem >Odgovori avtorju ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:814
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the composer window, inserts the quoted text from the currently "
"selected message, and sets the <guilabel>To:</guilabel> field to the "
"preferred reply-to address of the sender. The sending identity will "
"automatically be set to the identity to which this message was addressed."
msgstr ""
"Odpre okno za sestavljanje, vstavi citirano besedilo iz trenutno izbranega "
"sporočila in nastavi polje <guilabel>Za:</guilabel> na prednostni naslov za "
"odgovor pošiljatelja. Identiteta pošiljatelja bo samodejno nastavljena na "
"identiteto, na katero je bilo to sporočilo naslovljeno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:821
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>L</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Message</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Reply Special &gt;</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Reply to "
"Mailing-List...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>L</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Sporočilo</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Poseben odgovor &gt;</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Odgovori "
"poštnemu seznamu ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:824
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the composer window, inserts the quoted text of the currently selected "
"message, and sets the <guilabel>To:</guilabel> field to the mailing-list "
"address. If you did not specify a mailing-list address for the currently "
"selected folder and &kmail; cannot determine the posting address from the "
"currently selected message, the <guilabel>To:</guilabel> field will be "
"empty. The sending identity will automatically be set to the identity to "
"which this message was addressed."
msgstr ""
"Odpre okno za sestavljanje, vstavi citirano besedilo trenutno izbranega "
"sporočila in nastavi polje <guilabel>Za:</guilabel> na naslov poštnega "
"seznama. Če niste podali naslova poštnega seznama za trenutno izbrano mapo "
"in &kmail; ne more določiti naslova za objavo iz trenutno izbranega "
"sporočila, bo polje <guilabel>Za:</guilabel> prazno. Identiteta pošiljatelja "
"bo samodejno nastavljena na identiteto, na katero je bilo to sporočilo "
"naslovljeno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:833
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Message</guimenu><guisubmenu>Reply Special &gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Reply Without Quote...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guisubmenu>Posebni odgovor &gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem >Odgovori brez citata ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:836
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Works just like <guimenuitem>Reply...</guimenuitem>, except that the text of "
"the currently selected message is not quoted."
msgstr ""
"Deluje tako kot <guimenuitem >Odgovori ...</guimenuitem >, le da besedilo "
"trenutno izbranega sporočila ni citirano."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:841
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Message</guimenu><guisubmenu>Reply Special &gt;</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Reply With Custom Template</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guisubmenu>Posebni odgovor &gt;</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Odgovori s predlogo po meri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:843
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Works just like <guimenuitem>Reply...</guimenuitem> with an added option: "
"you may select a custom template configured via <link linkend=\"configure-"
"composer-custom-templates\">Custom Templates</link>."
msgstr ""
"Deluje tako kot <guimenuitem>Odgovori ...</guimenuitem> z dodano možnostjo: "
"izberete lahko predlogo po meri, konfigurirano prek <link linkend="
"\"configure-composer-custom-templates\">Predloge po meri</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:848
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Message</guimenu><guisubmenu>Reply Special &gt;</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Reply to All With Custom Template</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guisubmenu>Poseben odgovor &gt;</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Odgovori vsem s predlogo po meri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:850
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Works just like <guimenuitem>Reply to All...</guimenuitem> with an added "
"option: you may select a custom template configured via <link linkend="
"\"configure-composer-custom-templates\">Custom Templates</link>."
msgstr ""
"Deluje tako kot <guimenuitem>Odgovori vsem ...</guimenuitem> z dodano "
"možnostjo: izberete lahko predlogo po meri, konfigurirano prek <link linkend="
"\"configure-composer-custom-templates\">Predloge po meri</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:856
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Message</guimenu><guisubmenu>Forward &gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>As Attachment</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guisubmenu>Posreduj &gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem> Kot priloga</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:859
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Forwards the message to a new recipient. The message and its attachments "
"will be attached to the new message. The original message headers will be "
"included in the forwarded message."
msgstr ""
"Posreduje sporočilo novemu prejemniku. Sporočilo in njegove priloge bodo "
"priložene novemu sporočilu. Izvirne glave sporočil bodo vključene v "
"posredovano sporočilo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:864
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Message</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Forward &gt;</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Inline</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Sporočilo</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Posreduj &gt;</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Inline</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:866
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The message's text and some important header fields will be copied to the "
"body of the new message, with text marking where the forwarded part begins. "
"Attachments will be attached to the new message."
msgstr ""
"Besedilo sporočila in nekatera pomembna polja glave bodo kopirani v telo "
"novega sporočila, pri čemer bo besedilo označeno, kje se začne posredovani "
"del. Novemu sporočilu bodo priložene priloge."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:871
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>E</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Message</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Forward &gt;</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Redirect</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>E</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Sporočilo</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Posreduj &gt;</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Preusmeri</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:873
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This works like \"Forward\", except that the message stays the same (even "
"the <guilabel>From:</guilabel> field). The user who redirected the message "
"is identified by special header fields (<literal>Redirect-From</literal>, "
"<literal>Redirect-Date</literal>, <literal>Redirect-To</literal>, &etc;)."
msgstr ""
"To deluje kot \"Posreduj\", le da sporočilo ostane isto (celo polje "
"<guilabel>Od:</guilabel>). Uporabnik, ki je preusmeril sporočilo, je "
"identificiran s posebnimi polji glave (<literal>Preusmeritev-Od</literal>, "
"<literal>Datum-Preusmeritve</literal>, <literal>Preusmeri-Na</literal> "
"&etc;)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:880
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Message</guimenu><guisubmenu>Forward &gt;</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>With Custom Template</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guisubmenu>Posreduj &gt;</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>S predlogo po meri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:882
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Works just like \"Forward\", but gives you the option to select a custom "
"template configured via the composer custom templates tab in <link linkend="
"\"configure-composer-custom-templates\">Custom Templates</link>."
msgstr ""
"Deluje tako kot »Posreduj«, vendar vam daje možnost, da izberete predlogo po "
"meri, konfigurirano prek zavihka predloge po meri skladatelja v <link "
"linkend=\"configure-composer-custom-templates\">Predloge po meri</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:889
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Send Again...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pošlji ponovno ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:890
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a composer window with the currently selected message so it can be "
"sent again."
msgstr ""
"Odpre okno skladatelja s trenutno izbranim sporočilom, da ga je mogoče znova "
"poslati."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:891
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu item is only available for messages which you have sent or, more "
"precisely, for messages which have the <guilabel>sent</guilabel> status. If "
"you wish to resend some other message, double-click its entry in the message "
"list. Or view the message and use the <keycap>T</keycap> shortcut. You may "
"also do this by adding an <guibutton>Edit as New</guibutton> button to the "
"toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Ta menijska postavka je na voljo samo za sporočila, ki ste jih poslali, ali, "
"natančneje, za sporočila, ki imajo status <guilabel>poslano</guilabel>. Če "
"želite ponovno poslati kakšno drugo sporočilo, dvakrat kliknite njegov vnos "
"na seznamu sporočil. Ali pa si oglejte sporočilo in uporabite bližnjico "
"<keycap>T</keycap>. To lahko storite tudi tako, da v orodno vrstico dodate "
"gumb <guibutton>Uredi kot novo</guibutton>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:905
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Mailing List Name: &gt;</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Ime poštnega seznama: &gt;</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:907
#, no-c-format
msgid "Offers several options for mailing list messages."
msgstr "Ponuja več možnosti za sporočila na poštnem seznamu."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:908
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The current working folder must be configured as a mailing list for this "
"option to be available. Please see <link linkend=\"folders-properties-"
"mailinglist\">Folder Properties Mailing List</link> to learn about setting "
"up mailing lists."
msgstr ""
"Trenutna delovna mapa mora biti konfigurirana kot poštni seznam, da bo ta "
"možnost na voljo. Oglejte si <link linkend=\"folders-properties-mailinglist"
"\">poštni seznam lastnosti mape</link>, če želite izvedeti več o nastavitvi "
"poštnih seznamov."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:912
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following options are available in mailing list folders:"
msgstr "V mapah poštnega seznama so na voljo naslednje možnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:915
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Post New Message(email)</guimenuitem> will set the <guilabel>To:"
"</guilabel> address to the address configured as \"Post to List\"."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Objavi novo sporočilo(e-pošta)</guimenuitem> bo nastavil naslov "
"<guilabel>Za:</guilabel> na naslov, konfiguriran kot \"Objavi na seznam\"."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:917
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Request Help(email)</guimenuitem> will set the <guilabel>To:</"
"guilabel> address to the address configured in \"Post to List\" and will "
"place the word <literal>help</literal> in the <guilabel>Subject:</guilabel> "
"field."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Zahtevaj pomoč(e-pošta)</guimenuitem> bo naslov <guilabel>Za:</"
"guilabel> nastavil na naslov, konfiguriran v »Objavi na seznamu«, in besedo "
"<literal>pomoč</literal> postavil v Polje <guilabel>Zadeva:</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:920
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Subscribe to List(web)</guimenuitem> will point your default "
"web browser to the \"subscribe\" web site of the configured mailing list."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Naroči se na seznam (splet)</guimenuitem> bo vaš privzeti "
"spletni brskalnik usmeril na spletno mesto za \"naročanje\" konfiguriranega "
"poštnega seznama."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:922
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Subscribe to List(email)</guimenuitem> will set the "
"<guilabel>To:</guilabel> address to the mailing list subscription address, "
"and place the word <literal>subscribe</literal> in the <guilabel>Subject:</"
"guilabel> field."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Naroči se na seznam (e-pošta)</guimenuitem> bo nastavil naslov "
"<guilabel>Za:</guilabel> na naslov naročnine na poštni seznam in besedo "
"<literal>naroči se</literal> v <guilabel> Zadeva:</guilabel> polje."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:925
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Unsubscribe from List(web)</guimenuitem> will point your "
"default web browser to the \"unsubscribe\" web site of the configured "
"mailing list."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Odjava s seznama(splet)</guimenuitem> bo vaš privzeti spletni "
"brskalnik usmeril na spletno mesto za \"odjavo\" konfiguriranega poštnega "
"seznama."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:927
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Unsubscribe from List(email)</guimenuitem> will set the "
"<guilabel>To:</guilabel> address to the mailing list subscription address, "
"and place the word <literal>unsubscribe</literal> in the <guilabel>Subject:</"
"guilabel> field."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Odjava s seznama (e-pošta)</guimenuitem> bo naslov <guilabel>Za:"
"</guilabel> nastavil na naslov naročnine na poštni seznam in besedo "
"<literal>odjava</literal> postavil v <guilabel> Zadeva:</guilabel> polje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:936
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Message</guimenu><guisubmenu>Copy Message To &gt;</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guisubmenu>Kopiraj sporočilo v &gt;</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:937
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copies the selected message(s) to a specified folder. You may choose from "
"recent folders, local folders, or a specific &IMAP; account folder."
msgstr ""
"Kopira izbrana sporočila v določeno mapo. Izbirate lahko med nedavnimi "
"mapami, lokalnimi mapami ali določenim &IMAP; mapo računa."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:942
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Message</guimenu><guisubmenu>Move Message To &gt;</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guisubmenu>Premakni sporočilo v &gt;</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:943
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The same as \"Copy Message To\", above, except this option will permanently "
"move the selected message(s) to the chosen folder."
msgstr ""
"Enako kot \"Kopiraj sporočilo v\" zgoraj, le da bo ta možnost trajno "
"premaknila izbrana sporočila v izbrano mapo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:949
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Message</guimenu><guisubmenu>Mark Message &gt;</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guisubmenu>Označi sporočilo &gt;</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:950
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lets you change the status of the selected message to one of the following "
"values:"
msgstr ""
"Omogoča vam, da spremenite stanje izbranega sporočila na eno od naslednjih "
"vrednosti:"

#. Tag: entry
#: menus.docbook:952 menus.docbook:1003
#, no-c-format
msgid "Status"
msgstr "Stanje"

#. Tag: entry
#: menus.docbook:952 menus.docbook:1003
#, no-c-format
msgid "Symbol"
msgstr "Simbol"

#. Tag: entry
#: menus.docbook:952 menus.docbook:1003
#, no-c-format
msgid "Meaning"
msgstr "Pomen"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:956
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Mark Message as Read</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Označi sporočilo kot prebrano</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: entry
#: menus.docbook:960
#, no-c-format
msgid "The message has been read."
msgstr "Sporočilo je prebrano."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:963
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>U</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Mark Message as Unread</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>U</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Označi sporočilo kot neprebrano</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: entry
#: menus.docbook:967
#, no-c-format
msgid "The message has not been read yet."
msgstr "Sporočilo še ni prebrano."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: menus.docbook:970
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mark Message as Important"
msgstr "Označi sporočilo kot pomembno"

#. Tag: entry
#: menus.docbook:973
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This status will not automatically be set by &kmail;. You can use it freely "
"to mark messages that are in some way important to you."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; tega stanja ne bo samodejno nastavil. Z njim lahko poljubno označite "
"sporočila, ki so vam na nek način pomembna."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: menus.docbook:977
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove Important Mark"
msgstr "Odstrani pomembno oznako"

#. Tag: entry
#: menus.docbook:980
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removes a previously set important flag from the message."
msgstr "Odstrani predhodno nastavljeno pomembno zastavico iz sporočila."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: menus.docbook:983
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mark Message as Action Item"
msgstr "Označi sporočilo kot dejanje"

#. Tag: entry
#: menus.docbook:986
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This status will not automatically be set by &kmail;. Use this to mark "
"messages that are action items; &eg;, a to-do list."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; tega stanja ne bo samodejno nastavil. Uporabite to za označevanje "
"sporočil, ki so dejanja; &eg; seznam opravil."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: menus.docbook:989
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove Action Item Mark"
msgstr "Odstrani oznako elementa dejanja"

#. Tag: entry
#: menus.docbook:992
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removes a previously set action item mark from the message."
msgstr "Odstrani predhodno nastavljeno oznako elementa dejanja iz sporočila."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1000
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Message</guimenu><guisubmenu>Mark Thread</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guisubmenu>Označi nit</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1001
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lets you change the status of all messages in a thread as follows:"
msgstr "Omogoča spreminjanje statusa vseh sporočil v niti na naslednji način:"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: menus.docbook:1007
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mark Thread as Read"
msgstr "Označi nit kot prebrano"

#. Tag: entry
#: menus.docbook:1010
#, no-c-format
msgid "The entire thread has been read."
msgstr "Celotna nit je bila prebrana."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: menus.docbook:1013
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mark Thread as Unread"
msgstr "Označi nit kot neprebrano"

#. Tag: entry
#: menus.docbook:1016
#, no-c-format
msgid "The thread has not been read yet."
msgstr "Tema še ni bila prebrana."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: menus.docbook:1019
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mark Thread as Important"
msgstr "Označi nit kot pomembno"

#. Tag: entry
#: menus.docbook:1022
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This status will not automatically be set by &kmail;. You can use it freely "
"to mark threads that are in some way important to you."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; tega stanja ne bo samodejno nastavil. Lahko ga prosto uporabljate za "
"označevanje niti, ki so vam na nek način pomembne."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: menus.docbook:1026
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove Important Thread Mark"
msgstr "Odstranite oznako pomembne niti"

#. Tag: entry
#: menus.docbook:1029
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removes a previously set \"important\" flag from the thread."
msgstr "Odstrani predhodno nastavljeno oznako »pomembno« iz niti."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: menus.docbook:1032
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mark Thread as Action Item"
msgstr "Označi nit kot element dejanja"

#. Tag: entry
#: menus.docbook:1035
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This status will not automatically be set by &kmail;. Use this to mark "
"threads that are action items (&eg;, a to-do list)."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; tega stanja ne bo samodejno nastavil. Uporabite to za označevanje "
"niti, ki so elementi dejanja (&eg; seznam opravil)."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: menus.docbook:1039
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove Action Item Thread Mark"
msgstr "Odstrani oznako niti dejanja"

#. Tag: entry
#: menus.docbook:1042
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removes a previously set action item mark from the thread."
msgstr "Odstrani predhodno nastavljeno oznako elementa dejanja iz niti."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: menus.docbook:1045
#, no-c-format
msgid "Watch Thread"
msgstr "Oglejte si nit"

#. Tag: entry
#: menus.docbook:1048
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the watched thread status, which lets you easily view threads you're "
"interested in by selecting the <guimenu>Watched</guimenu> status in the drop "
"down box found in the Quick Search Bar. (Click on the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"view-filter.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> icon to display the "
"filterable categories.)"
msgstr ""
"Nastavi status opazovane niti, ki vam omogoča preprost ogled niti, ki vas "
"zanimajo, tako da izberete status <guimenu>Ogledano</guimenu> v spustnem "
"polju v vrstici za hitro iskanje. (Kliknite ikono "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"view-filter.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> za prikaz kategorij, ki "
"jih je mogoče filtrirati.)"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: menus.docbook:1054
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore Thread"
msgstr "Prezri nit"

#. Tag: entry
#: menus.docbook:1057
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allows you to ignore entire threads."
msgstr "Omogoča, da prezrete celotne niti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1065
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Message</guimenu><guisubmenu>Create Filter</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guisubmenu>Ustvari filter</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1066
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the <link linkend=\"filter-dialog-id\">Filter dialog</link> with a new "
"filter added. This new filter is based on fields in the current message, "
"depending on the submenu item you select:"
msgstr ""
"Odpre <link linkend=\"filter-dialog-id\">pogovorno okno filtra</link> z "
"dodanim novim filtrom. Ta novi filter temelji na poljih v trenutnem "
"sporočilu, odvisno od elementa podmenija, ki ga izberete:"

#. Tag: member
#: menus.docbook:1069
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filter on Subject..."
msgstr "Filtriraj po temi ..."

#. Tag: member
#: menus.docbook:1070
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filter on From..."
msgstr "Filtriraj po Od ..."

#. Tag: member
#: menus.docbook:1071
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filter on To..."
msgstr "Filtriraj po Za ..."

#. Tag: member
#: menus.docbook:1072
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Filter on Mailing-List...(currently selected message must be a mailing list "
"for this to be available)."
msgstr ""
"Filtriraj na poštnem seznamu ... (trenutno izbrano sporočilo mora biti "
"poštni seznam, da je na voljo)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1077
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Apply Filter</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Uporabi filter</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1078
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lets you <guimenuitem>Apply all Filters</guimenuitem>. If you have spam "
"filtering set up via the <link linkend=\"the-anti-spam-wizard\">Anti-Spam "
"Wizard</link>, the options <guimenuitem>Classify as Spam</guimenuitem> and "
"<guimenuitem>Classify as NOT Spam</guimenuitem> will also be available here."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča <guimenuitem>uporabo vseh filtrov</guimenuitem>. Če imate "
"filtriranje neželene pošte nastavljeno prek <link linkend=\"the-anti-spam-"
"wizard\">čarovnika za zaščito pred neželeno pošto</link>, sta možnosti "
"<guimenuitem>Razvrsti kot neželeno pošto</guimenuitem> in "
"<guimenuitem>Razvrsti kot Tukaj bo na voljo tudi NI vsiljena pošta</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>V</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Message</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>View Source</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>V</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Sporočilo</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Ogled vira</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows the message and its complete headers in plain text format in a new "
"window. This can help you figure out where a message really came from."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže sporočilo in njegove celotne glave v obliki navadnega besedila v "
"novem oknu. To vam lahko pomaga ugotoviti, od kod sporočilo v resnici "
"prihaja."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You should be aware that it is easy to fake, or spoof, the <literal>From:</"
"literal> header in a message. You can always find out which mail servers "
"were used to send the message by examining the <literal>Received:</literal> "
"lines in the message headers."
msgstr ""
"Zavedati se morate, da je glavo <literal>Od:</literal> v sporočilu enostavno "
"ponarediti. Vedno lahko ugotovite, kateri poštni strežniki so bili "
"uporabljeni za pošiljanje sporočila, tako da pregledate vrstice "
"<literal>Prejeto:</literal> v glavah sporočil."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>D</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Message "
"Structure</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>D</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži "
"strukturo sporočila</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays the structure viewer, an area below the preview pane that lets you "
"view each &MIME; component of a message separately. This item will only be "
"present if the <link linkend=\"configure-plugins-tools\">Expert Plugin</"
"link> has been activated."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže pregledovalnik strukture, območje pod podoknom za predogled, ki vam "
"omogoča ogled vsakega &MIME; komponento sporočila ločeno. Ta element bo "
"prisoten samo, če je bil aktiviran <link linkend=\"configure-plugins-tools"
"\">strokovni vtičnik</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:1123 menus.docbook:1928
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tools Menu"
msgstr "Meni Orodja"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: menus.docbook:1125 menus.docbook:1930
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Tools Menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Meni Orodja</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: menus.docbook:1131 menus.docbook:1936
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Tools Menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Meni Orodja</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1134 menus.docbook:1939
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>The Tools Menu</para>"
msgstr "<para>Meni Orodja</para>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>S</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Find Messages...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>S</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Poišči sporočila ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a search window that lets you search for messages with certain "
"characteristics, &eg;, a certain subject. Please see <link linkend=\"filter-"
"criteria\">Filter Criteria</link> for details on search options."
msgstr ""
"Odpre iskalno okno, ki vam omogoča iskanje sporočil z določenimi "
"značilnostmi, &eg; določeno temo. Za podrobnosti o možnostih iskanja si "
"oglejte <link linkend=\"filter-criteria\">Kriterije filtra</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1148
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Your search results will be displayed in the text area; you may either "
"<guibutton>Open Search Folder</guibutton> to see a folder containing the "
"messages that were located, or highlight the desired message and select "
"<guibutton>Open Message</guibutton>. Additional actions are available via a "
"context menu, which can be activated by clicking the &RMB;."
msgstr ""
"Vaši rezultati iskanja bodo prikazani v besedilnem območju; lahko "
"<guibutton>Odprete iskalno mapo</guibutton>, da vidite mapo, ki vsebuje "
"najdena sporočila, ali pa označite želeno sporočilo in izberete "
"<guibutton>Odpri sporočilo</guibutton>. Dodatna dejanja so na voljo v "
"kontekstnem meniju, ki ga lahko aktivirate s klikom &RMB;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1155
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Address Book</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Imenik</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Starts <ulink url=\"help:kaddressbook\">&kaddressbook;</ulink>, the &kde; "
"email address / personal contact information management program."
msgstr ""
"Zažene <ulink url=\"help:kaddressbook\">&kaddressbook;</ulink>, &kde; "
"program za upravljanje elektronskih naslovov/osebnih kontaktnih podatkov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1161
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Certificate Manager</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Upravitelj potrdil</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Starts <ulink url=\"help:kleopatra\">&kleopatra;</ulink>, the &kde; "
"certificate manager."
msgstr ""
"Zažene <ulink url=\"help:kleopatra\">&kleopatra;</ulink>, &kde; upravitelj "
"certifikatov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guisubmenu>Edit \"Out of Office\" Replies...</"
"guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guisubmenu>Urejanje odgovorov »Odsoten« ...</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Launches the <guilabel>Configure \"Out of Office\" Replies</guilabel> "
"dialog, which allows you to set up vacation notifications."
msgstr ""
"Zažene pogovorno okno <guilabel>Konfiguriraj odgovore »Odsoten«</guilabel>, "
"ki vam omogoča nastavitev obvestil o dopustu."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Out of Office reply</guilabel> functionality relies on server-side "
"filtering. To use it you must configure the <link linkend=\"receiving-mail"
"\">Filtering tab</link> (see options relevant to a &kolab; server) of your "
"&IMAP; account set-up."
msgstr ""
"Funkcionalnost <guilabel>Odgovor o odsotnosti</guilabel> temelji na "
"filtriranju na strani strežnika. Če ga želite uporabljati, morate "
"konfigurirati <link linkend=\"receiving-mail\">zavihek Filtriranje</link> "
"(glejte možnosti, ki se nanašajo na strežnik &kolab;) vašega &IMAP; "
"nastavitev računa."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1185
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guisubmenu>Filter Log Viewer...</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guisubmenu>Pregledovalnik dnevnika filtrov ...</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the viewer window for the filter log; there you will find some options "
"to control the logging of the filtering process. In the log you will find "
"valuable information about the filter rules used, the result of evaluating "
"those rules, and which filter actions were applied to a particular message."
msgstr ""
"Odpre okno pregledovalnika za dnevnik filtra; tam boste našli nekaj možnosti "
"za nadzor beleženja postopka filtriranja. V dnevniku boste našli dragocene "
"informacije o uporabljenih pravilih filtra, rezultatu ocenjevanja teh pravil "
"in dejanjih filtra, ki so bila uporabljena za določeno sporočilo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guisubmenu>Import from another Email Client...</"
"guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guisubmenu>Uvoz iz drugega e-poštnega odjemalca ..."
"</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Launches the Akonadi Import Wizard dialog, which assists in importing "
"settings and email from a wide variety of email clients. Please see the "
"<ulink url=\"help:/importwizard\">Import Wizard</ulink> documentation for "
"details."
msgstr ""
"Zažene pogovorno okno čarovnika za uvoz Akonadi, ki pomaga pri uvažanju "
"nastavitev in e-pošte iz številnih e-poštnih odjemalcev. Za podrobnosti "
"glejte dokumentacijo <ulink url=\"help:/importwizard\">čarovnika za uvoz</"
"ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Close &kmail; before importing data. The wizard may modify &kmail;'s "
"configuration file, and can cause unpredictable results if you attempt to "
"import data while &kmail; is running."
msgstr ""
"Zapri &kmail; pred uvozom podatkov. Čarovnik lahko spremeni konfiguracijsko "
"datoteko &kmail; in lahko povzroči nepredvidljive rezultate, če poskusite "
"uvoziti podatke, medtem ko &kmail; teče."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guisubmenu>Import/Export &kmail; Data...</"
"guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guisubmenu>Uvoz/izvoz &kmail; Podatki ...</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1205
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Launches the PIM Data Exporter dialog, which assists in exporting your "
"settings and email, or restoring them from a back up copy. Please see <ulink "
"url=\"help:/pimdataexporter\">Pim Data Exporter</ulink> for details."
msgstr ""
"Zažene pogovorno okno Izvoznika podatkov PIM, ki pomaga pri izvozu vaših "
"nastavitev in e-pošte ali pri obnovi iz varnostne kopije. Za podrobnosti si "
"oglejte <ulink url=\"help:/pimdataexporter\">Izvoznik podatkov Pim</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1211
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Log Activities...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Dnevnik dejavnosti ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Starts the Activity Logger, which logs certain activities. This option is "
"only available when the <guilabel>Log Activities</guilabel> plugin has been "
"loaded. Primarily for developers."
msgstr ""
"Zažene Activity Logger, ki beleži določene dejavnosti. Ta možnost je na "
"voljo le, ko je naložen vtičnik <guilabel>Dejavnosti dnevnika</guilabel>. "
"Predvsem za razvijalce."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1217
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Anti-Spam Wizard...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Čarovnik za zaščito pred vsiljeno "
"pošto...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Launches the Anti-Spam Wizard, which can help you set up spam filtering. "
"Please see <link linkend=\"the-anti-spam-wizard\">Anti-Spam Wizard</link> "
"for details. This option is only available when the <guilabel>Antispam</"
"guilabel> plugin has been loaded."
msgstr ""
"Zažene čarovnika za zaščito pred neželeno pošto, ki vam lahko pomaga "
"nastaviti filtriranje neželene pošte. Za podrobnosti si oglejte <link "
"linkend=\"the-anti-spam-wizard\">čarovnika za zaščito pred vsiljeno pošto</"
"link>. Ta možnost je na voljo le, če je naložen vtičnik <guilabel>Proti "
"neželeni pošti</guilabel>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1224
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Anti-Virus Wizard...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Protivirusni čarovnik ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Launches the Anti-Virus Wizard, which can help you set up anti-virus "
"scanning. Please see <link linkend=\"the-anti-virus-wizard\">Anti-Virus "
"Wizard</link> for details. This option is only available when the "
"<guilabel>Antivirus</guilabel> plugin has been loaded."
msgstr ""
"Zažene protivirusni čarovnik, ki vam lahko pomaga nastaviti protivirusno "
"skeniranje. Za podrobnosti si oglejte <link linkend=\"the-anti-virus-wizard"
"\">čarovnika za protivirusni program</link>. Ta možnost je na voljo samo, ko "
"je naložen vtičnik <guilabel>Protivirusni</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:1235 menus.docbook:1996
#, no-c-format
msgid "Settings Menu"
msgstr "Meni z nastavitvami"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: menus.docbook:1237 menus.docbook:1998
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Settings Menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Meni z nastavitvami</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: menus.docbook:1243 menus.docbook:2004
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Settings Menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Meni z nastavitvami</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1246 menus.docbook:2007
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>The Settings Menu</para>"
msgstr "<para>Meni z nastavitvami</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the menu item you are looking for is missing, please see <ulink url="
"\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">Settings Menu</ulink> in "
"&kde; Fundamentals. The items listed here are &kmail; specific."
msgstr ""
"Če menijski element, ki ga iščete, manjka, glejte <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">Meni z nastavitvami</ulink> v &kde; "
"Osnove. Tukaj navedeni elementi so &kmail; specifična."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Quick Search bar</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prikaži vrstico za hitro "
"iskanje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enables the Quick Search bar, which lets you quickly search for messages "
"matching your criteria."
msgstr ""
"Omogoči vrstico za hitro iskanje, ki vam omogoča hitro iskanje sporočil, ki "
"ustrezajo vašim kriterijem."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Filters...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj filtre ...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1266
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens the <link linkend=\"filters\">Message Filters</link> dialog."
msgstr "Odpre pogovorno okno <link linkend=\"filters\">Filtri sporočil</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1270
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Manage Sieve Scripts...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Upravljanje sijevnih skriptov ...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your mail server supports sieves (server side filtering), you may "
"configure those scripts here."
msgstr ""
"Če vaš poštni strežnik podpira sieves (filtriranje na strani strežnika), "
"lahko te skripte konfigurirate tukaj."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1276
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Add Account...</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Dodaj račun ...</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Starts the Account Wizard dialog, which assists in setting up new or "
"additional accounts. Please see <link linkend=\"account-wizard\">Account "
"Wizard</link> for details."
msgstr ""
"Zažene pogovorno okno čarovnika za račune, ki pomaga pri nastavljanju novih "
"ali dodatnih računov. Za podrobnosti si oglejte <link linkend=\"account-"
"wizard\">čarovnik za račun</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Automatic Archiving...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj samodejno "
"arhiviranje ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Initiates a dialog to set up automatic archiving. See <ulink url=\"help:/"
"akonadi_archivemail_agent\">Automatic Archiving</ulink> for details."
msgstr ""
"Odpre pogovorno okno za nastavitev samodejnega arhiviranja. Za podrobnosti "
"glejte <ulink url=\"help:/akonadi_archivemail_agent\">Samodejno arhiviranje</"
"ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &kmail;...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &kmail;...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1314
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the <link linkend=\"configure\">Configure &kmail;</link> dialog. There "
"are hundreds of variables to play with. Have fun!"
msgstr ""
"Odpre pogovorno okno <link linkend=\"configure\">Konfiguriraj &kmail;</"
"link>. Igrati se je na stotine spremenljivk. Zabavaj se!"

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:1323 menus.docbook:2036
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help Menu"
msgstr "Meni Pomoč"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: menus.docbook:1325 menus.docbook:2038
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Help Menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Meni Pomoč</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: menus.docbook:1331 menus.docbook:2044
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Help Menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Meni Pomoč</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1334 menus.docbook:2047
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>The Help Menu</para>"
msgstr "<para>Meni Pomoč</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1340
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help\">Help "
"Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals, with one additional item."
msgstr ""
"To je <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help\">meni Pomoč</"
"ulink> programa &kde; Osnove, z eno dodatno točko."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1345
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Help</guimenu><guimenuitem>&kmail; Introduction</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu><guimenuitem>&kmail; Uvod</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1346
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens the <link linkend=\"intro\">Introduction</link> welcome screen."
msgstr "Odpre pozdravni zaslon <link linkend=\"intro\">Uvod</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:1353
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &kmail; Composer Window"
msgstr "&kmail; Okno skladatelja"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>New Composer</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nov skladatelj</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1377
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens a new composer window so you can create a message."
msgstr "Odpre novo okno skladatelja, da lahko ustvarite sporočilo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1397
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Return</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Send Mail</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Nazaj</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pošlji pošto</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1399
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sends the message immediately. If you use &SMTP; to send your messages and "
"the &SMTP; server is not reachable, the message will remain in the outbox "
"and you will get an error message. After the connection issues have been "
"resolved, you can send the messages in the outbox using <link linkend="
"\"reader-send-queued-messages\"><menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Send Queued Messages</guimenuitem></menuchoice></link> "
"(in the reader window)."
msgstr ""
"Takoj pošlje sporočilo. Če uporabljate &SMTP; za pošiljanje sporočil in "
"&SMTP; strežnik ni dosegljiv, bo sporočilo ostalo v mapi za pošiljanje in "
"prejeli boste sporočilo o napaki. Ko so težave s povezavo odpravljene, lahko "
"pošljete sporočila v mapo za pošiljanje z <link linkend=\"reader-send-queued-"
"messages\"><menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pošlji "
"sporočila v čakalni vrsti</guimenuitem></menuchoice></link> (v oknu "
"bralnika)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1407
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Send Mail Via &gt;</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pošlji pošto prek &gt;</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to specify which outgoing mail server will be used to send the "
"message."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča vam, da določite, kateri strežnik odhodne pošte bo uporabljen za "
"pošiljanje sporočila."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1412
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Send Later</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pošlji pozneje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1413
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Launches the send later dialog. Please see the <ulink url=\"help:/"
"akonadi_sendlater_agent\">Send Later</ulink> documentation for details."
msgstr ""
"Zažene pogovorno okno za pošiljanje pozneje. Za podrobnosti glejte "
"dokumentacijo <ulink url=\"help:/akonadi_sendlater_agent\">Pošlji pozneje</"
"ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1418
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Send Later Via &gt;</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pošlji pozneje prek &gt;</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1419
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to specify which outgoing mail server will be used to send the "
"delayed message."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča vam, da določite, kateri strežnik odhodne pošte bo uporabljen za "
"pošiljanje zakasnjenega sporočila."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1424
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save as File</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani kot datoteko</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1425
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Saves the message as a file. Three formats are supported: Rich Text (.html), "
"plain text (.txt), and Open Document Format (.odt)."
msgstr ""
"Shrani sporočilo kot datoteko. Podprti so trije formati: Rich Text (.html), "
"golo besedilo (.txt) in Open Document Format (.odt)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1430
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save as Draft</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani kot osnutek</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1432
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Saves the message in the <guilabel>drafts</guilabel> folder so you can "
"finish it later."
msgstr ""
"Shrani sporočilo v mapo <guilabel>osnutki</guilabel>, da ga lahko dokončate "
"pozneje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1437
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save as Template</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani kot predlogo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1438
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lets you save your message as a template. Please see <link linkend=\"new-"
"compose-from-templates\">Compose from templates</link> for more information."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča shranjevanje sporočila kot predloge. Za več informacij glejte <link "
"linkend=\"new-compose-from-templates\">Sestavljanje iz predlog</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1443
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Insert Text File...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Vstavi besedilno datoteko ...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1444
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inserts a text file into the message text, starting at the cursor position."
msgstr ""
"V besedilo sporočila vstavi besedilno datoteko, začenši na položaju kazalke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1448
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Insert Recent Text File &gt;</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Vstavi nedavno besedilno datoteko "
"&gt;</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lets you choose from a list of recently inserted text files, and inserts "
"that file into your message. Select <guimenuitem>Clear List</guimenuitem> to "
"clear the list."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča izbiro s seznama nedavno vstavljenih besedilnih datotek in "
"vstavljanje te datoteke v vaše sporočilo. Izberite <guimenuitem>Počisti "
"seznam</guimenuitem>, da počistite seznam."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1454
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Print Preview</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Predogled tiskanja</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1455
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a print preview window and displays your message, formatted for "
"printing."
msgstr ""
"Odpre okno za predogled tiskanja in prikaže vaše sporočilo, oblikovano za "
"tiskanje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1459
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Print...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Natisni ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1461
#, no-c-format
msgid "Formats and prints the message you have composed."
msgstr "Oblikuje in natisne sporočilo, ki ste ga sestavili."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Share Mail Text... &gt;</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Deli besedilo pošte ... &gt;</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1466
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lets you make a second copy of your message somewhere else. Four options are "
"provided: Nextcloud (an OSS file-sharing app), Pastebin <ulink url=\"https://"
"pastebin.com\">(a freely available web site)</ulink>, Bluetooth, and Email "
"(opens another composer window, and adds the current message to that new "
"message, as an attachment). This option is not available unless the "
"<guilabel>Share Text</guilabel> plugin is active."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča vam, da naredite drugo kopijo svojega sporočila nekje drugje. Na "
"voljo so štiri možnosti: Nextcloud (aplikacija za skupno rabo datotek OSS), "
"Pastebin <ulink url=\"https://pastebin.com\">(prosto dostopno spletno "
"mesto)</ulink>, Bluetooth in E-pošta (odpre drug skladatelj in temu novemu "
"sporočilu doda trenutno sporočilo kot prilogo). Ta možnost ni na voljo, "
"razen če je aktiven vtičnik <guilabel>Deli besedilo</guilabel>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1474
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Message</guimenu><guimenuitem>Close</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>W</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Sporočilo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1476
#, no-c-format
msgid "Closes this composer window."
msgstr "Zapre to okno skladatelja."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1502
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the menu item you are looking for is missing, please see the <ulink url="
"\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-edit\">Edit Menu</ulink> section of "
"the &kde; Fundamentals Handbook. The items listed here are &kmail; specific."
msgstr ""
"Če menijski element, ki ga iščete, manjka, si oglejte razdelek <ulink url="
"\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-edit\">Meni Uredi</ulink> v &kde; "
"Priročnik o osnovah. Tukaj navedeni elementi so &kmail; specifična."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1508
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>O</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Paste as Quotation</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>O</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prilepi kot citat</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pastes the text from the clipboard and marks it as a quotation (&ie;, each "
"line preceded by \"&gt;\" and a space)."
msgstr ""
"Prilepi besedilo iz odložišča in ga označi kot citat (&ie;, pred vsako "
"vrstico sta \"&gt;\" in presledek)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1515
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Paste as Attachment</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prilepi kot prilogo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1516
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pastes a file that has been copied to the clipboard (&eg;, by using the "
"&dolphin; file manager) as an attachment."
msgstr ""
"Prilepi datoteko, ki je bila kopirana v odložišče (&eg; z uporabo "
"upravitelja datotek &dolphin;) kot prilogo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1521
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>V</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Paste Without "
"Formatting</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>V</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prilepi brez "
"oblikovanja</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1523
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pastes data from the clipboard as plain text, with no &HTML; formatting."
msgstr ""
"Prilepi podatke iz odložišča kot navadno besedilo, brez &HTML; oblikovanje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1527
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Clean Spaces</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Čisti prostori</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1528
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option supposedly replaces multiple adjacent newline characters or "
"spaces with single line breaks / spaces, but in testing, it apparently does "
"absolutely nothing."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost naj bi zamenjala več sosednjih znakov nove vrstice ali presledkov "
"z enojnimi prelomi vrstic/presledki, vendar pri testiranju očitno ne naredi "
"popolnoma nič."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1533
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Add Quote Characters</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Dodaj znake citatov</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1534
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Prepends each line of the selected text with the quotation indicator (&gt; "
"and a space, by default). If no selection is made, adds the indicator to "
"every line in the message."
msgstr ""
"Pred vsako vrstico izbranega besedila doda indikator narekovajev (&gt; in "
"presledek, privzeto). Če ni izbrana nobena izbira, doda indikator v vsako "
"vrstico v sporočilu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1539
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Remove Quote Characters</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Odstrani znake citatov</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1540
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removes the left-most quotation indicator from the selected text."
msgstr "Odstrani skrajni levi indikator narekovajev iz izbranega besedila."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1544
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Insert Email...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Vstavi e-pošto ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1545
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays a list of all the names in your address book, then inserts the "
"chosen email address at the cursor position (after you make a selection and "
"click the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> button). This option is only available "
"when the <guimenuitem>Insert Email</guimenuitem> plugin has been loaded."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže seznam vseh imen v vašem imeniku, nato vstavi izbrani e-poštni "
"naslov na položaj kazalke (ko izberete in kliknete gumb <guibutton>V redu</"
"guibutton>). Ta možnost je na voljo le, če je naložen vtičnik "
"<guimenuitem>Vstavi e-pošto</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1551
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Space;</keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Insert Non Breaking Space</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Space;</keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Vstavi neprekinjen presledek</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1553
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inserts a non breaking space at the cursor position. This option is only "
"available when the <guimenuitem>Insert Non Breaking Space</guimenuitem> "
"plugin has been loaded."
msgstr ""
"Na položaj kazalke vstavi neprekinjen presledek. Ta možnost je na voljo le, "
"če je naložen vtičnik <guimenuitem>Vstavi neprekinjeni presledek</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1574
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Insert Special Character...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Vstavi poseben znak ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1575
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lets you insert a special character at the cursor position. A large number "
"of Unicode characters are made available. This option is only provided if "
"the <guimenuitem>Insert Special Character</guimenuitem> plugin has been "
"activated."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča vstavljanje posebnega znaka na položaj kazalke. Na voljo je veliko "
"število znakov Unicode. Ta možnost je na voljo le, če je bil aktiviran "
"vtičnik <guimenuitem>Vstavi posebne znake</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1579
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu item was moved to the <guimenu>Insert</guimenu> menu in release "
"5.17. If you have activated the plugin, and this entry does not appear when "
"&kmail; is restarted, check the <guimenu>Insert</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Ta menijski element je bil v izdaji 5.17 premaknjen v meni <guimenu>Vstavi</"
"guimenu>. Če ste aktivirali vtičnik in se ta vnos ne prikaže, ko &kmail; se "
"znova zažene, preverite meni <guimenu>Vstavi</guimenu>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1585
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Change Case &gt;</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Spremeni velike in male črke &gt;</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1586
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Helps you modify the capitalization of the selected text. There are four "
"options: <guilabel>Uppercase</guilabel> (capitalizes the selected "
"characters), <guilabel>Lowercase</guilabel> (forces selected text to all "
"lower case), <guilabel>Sentence case</guilabel> (capitalizes the first "
"letter of the selection and makes the rest lower case), and "
"<guilabel>Reverse Case</guilabel> (converts capital letters to lower case, "
"and vice versa). This option is only provided if the <guimenuitem>Change "
"Case</guimenuitem> plugin has been activated. This menu item remains grayed "
"out until some snippet of text has been selected for modification."
msgstr ""
"Pomaga vam spremeniti velike črke izbranega besedila. Na voljo so štiri "
"možnosti: <guilabel>Velike črke</guilabel> (napiše izbrane znake z velikimi "
"črkami), <guilabel>Male črke</guilabel> (sili izbrano besedilo v vse male "
"črke), <guilabel>Velike črke</guilabel> (napiše z velikimi črkami prva črka "
"izbire, ostale pa naredi male črke) in <guilabel>Obratna črka</guilabel> "
"(pretvori velike črke v male in obratno). Ta možnost je na voljo le, če je "
"bil aktiviran vtičnik <guimenuitem>Spremeni male in male črke</guimenuitem>. "
"Ta element menija ostane zatemnjen, dokler ni izbran delček besedila za "
"spremembo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1596
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zoom... &gt;</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Povečava ... &gt;</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1597
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lets you zoom in or zoom out on the message you are composing. This is the "
"same function appearing as <menuchoice><guimenu>View</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Zoom &gt;</guisubmenu></menuchoice> in the message "
"preview window. This option is not available unless the <guimenuitem>Zoom "
"Text</guimenuitem> plugin has been loaded."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča vam, da povečate ali pomanjšate sporočilo, ki ga sestavljate. To je "
"ista funkcija, ki se prikaže kot <menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Povečava &gt;</guisubmenu></menuchoice> v oknu za "
"predogled sporočila. Ta možnost ni na voljo, razen če je bil naložen vtičnik "
"<guimenuitem>Povečava besedila</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1604
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guimenuitem>Variables &gt;</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Spremenljivke &gt;</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1605
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lets you insert the contents of a named field at the cursor position. You "
"may choose among <guilabel>To &gt;</guilabel>, <guilabel>From &gt;</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>CC &gt;</guilabel>, <guilabel>Attachment &gt;</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Date/Time &gt;</guilabel>, and <guilabel>Misc &gt;</"
"guilabel> (which has just one associated submenu item, \"Subject\"). There "
"is one notable quirk: the date/time displayed in the submenu selections is "
"fixed at the time the Composer window was opened, but the value actually "
"inserted in a message is taken from the system clock."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča vstavljanje vsebine imenovanega polja na položaj kazalke. Izbirate "
"lahko med <guilabel>Za &gt;</guilabel>, <guilabel>Od &gt;</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>CC &gt;</guilabel>, <guilabel>Priloga &gt;</guilabel>, <guilabel "
">Datum/čas &gt;</guilabel> in <guilabel>Razno &gt;</guilabel> (ki ima samo "
"en povezan element podmenija, \"Zadeva\"). Obstaja ena opazna posebnost: "
"datum/čas, prikazan v izbirah podmenija, je določen v času, ko je bilo "
"odprto okno Composer, vendar je vrednost, ki je dejansko vstavljena v "
"sporočilo, vzeta iz sistemske ure."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1636
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu lets you toggle the display of the header fields and a few other "
"items in the composer window. Selected items will be marked (check box "
"colored in) in the menu."
msgstr ""
"Ta meni vam omogoča preklapljanje med prikazom polj glave in nekaj drugih "
"elementov v oknu skladatelja. Izbrani elementi bodo v meniju označeni "
"(potrditveno polje obarvano)."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1639
#, no-c-format
msgid "Several options are available:"
msgstr "Na voljo je več možnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1643
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>All Fields</guimenuitem>. Displays all six of the following "
"fields."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Vsa polja</guimenuitem>. Prikaže vseh šest naslednjih polj."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1646
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Identity</guimenuitem>. If you have defined more than one "
"identity, this will be a drop down box."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Identiteta</guimenuitem>. Če ste definirali več kot eno "
"identiteto, bo to spustno polje."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1650
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Dictionary</guimenuitem> used for spell checking. If multiple "
"dictionaries are installed, this will be a drop down box."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Slovar</guimenuitem>, ki se uporablja za preverjanje črkovanja. "
"Če je nameščenih več slovarjev, bo to spustno polje."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1654
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Sent-Mail Folder</guimenuitem>. The <guilabel>&nbsp;"
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"document-open.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>&nbsp;</guilabel> button "
"appearing on the right when this option is checked opens a folder selection "
"dialog."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Mapa poslane pošte</guimenuitem>. Gumb <guilabel>&nbsp;"
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"document-open.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>&nbsp;</guilabel>, ki se "
"prikaže na desni, ko če je ta možnost označena, odpre pogovorno okno za "
"izbiro mape."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1659
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Mail Transport</guimenuitem>. If you have created more than one "
"outgoing account, this will be a drop down box."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Prenos pošte</guimenuitem>. Če ste ustvarili več kot en odhodni "
"račun, bo to spustno polje."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1663
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>From</guimenuitem>. The contents of this field may vary, "
"depending on the Identity you use."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Od</guimenuitem>. Vsebina tega polja se lahko razlikuje glede "
"na Identiteto, ki jo uporabljate."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1666
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Subject</guimenuitem>. Use this field to describe your message, "
"briefly."
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Zadeva</guimenuitem>. V tem polju na kratko opišite svoje "
"sporočilo."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1670
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>To <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"go-"
"down.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject></guilabel> "
"drop down box is always present at the top of the composer window. Use it to "
"select <guilabel>CC</guilabel>, <guilabel>BCC</guilabel>, and "
"<guilabel>Reply-To</guilabel> addresses, as needed. Please see <link linkend="
"\"composer-headers\">Composer Headers</link> for further details on message "
"headers."
msgstr ""
"Spustno polje <guilabel>V <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"go-down.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject></"
"guilabel> je vedno prisotno na vrhu okna skladatelja. Uporabite ga za izbiro "
"naslovov <guilabel>Kp</guilabel>, <guilabel>Skp</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Odgovori na</guilabel>, če je potrebno. Za nadaljnje podrobnosti o "
"glavah sporočil glejte <link linkend=\"composer-headers\">Glave skladatelja</"
"link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1680
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Use Fixed Font</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Uporabi fiksno pisavo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1681
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Uses a fixed width (monospaced) font to display the currently edited "
"message. The particular font to be used can be configured in the "
"<guilabel>Appearance</guilabel> section of &kmail;'s configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"Za prikaz trenutno urejenega sporočila uporablja pisavo s fiksno širino "
"(enoprostor). Posamezno pisavo, ki jo želite uporabiti, lahko nastavite v "
"razdelku <guilabel>Videz</guilabel> konfiguracijskega pogovornega okna "
"&kmail;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1687
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem>Snippets</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izrezki</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1688
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays a column on the right hand side of the composer window that allows "
"you to use and create snippets. Please see <link linkend=\"setup-text-"
"snippets\">Snippets</link> for more information."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže stolpec na desni strani okna skladatelja, ki vam omogoča uporabo in "
"ustvarjanje izrezkov. Za več informacij si oglejte <link linkend=\"setup-"
"text-snippets\">Izrezke</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:1698
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options Menu"
msgstr "Meni možnosti"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: menus.docbook:1700
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Options Menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Meni z možnostmi</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: menus.docbook:1706
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Options Menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Meni z možnostmi</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1709
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>The Options Menu</para>"
msgstr "<para>Meni z možnostmi</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1715
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu lets you toggle various options for the current message. Selected "
"items will be marked (check box colored in) in the menu."
msgstr ""
"Ta meni vam omogoča preklapljanje med različnimi možnostmi za trenutno "
"sporočilo. Izbrani elementi bodo v meniju označeni (potrditveno polje "
"obarvano)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1721
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Options</guimenu><guimenuitem>Urgent</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nujno</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1722
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the priority of the message to Urgent by inserting two header lines: "
"\"X-PRIORITY: 2 (High)\" and \"Priority: urgent\". The receiver's email "
"client must provide support for these headers; otherwise they will have no "
"effect. &kmail; itself does not support priorities for incoming messages "
"(although you can <link linkend=\"reader-mark-messages\">mark messages</"
"link> as Important)."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi prioriteto sporočila na Nujno tako, da vstavi dve vrstici glave: \"X-"
"PRIORITETA: 2 (visoka)\" in \"Prioriteta: nujno\". Prejemnikov e-poštni "
"odjemalec mora zagotoviti podporo za te glave; sicer ne bodo imeli učinka. "
"&kmail; samo po sebi ne podpira prioritet za dohodna sporočila (čeprav lahko "
"<link linkend=\"reader-mark-messages\">sporočila označite</link> kot "
"pomembna)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1730
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Options</guimenu><guimenuitem>Request Disposition Notification</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zahtevaj obvestilo o odstranitvi</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1732
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you choose this option, &kmail; will insert a Disposition-Notification-"
"To: header line in the message, which is a request to receive an email "
"notification once your message has been downloaded and read by the "
"recipient. This function must be supported, and enabled by the receiver's "
"email client; otherwise, it will not work."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete to možnost, &kmail; bo v sporočilo vstavil naslovno vrstico "
"Disposition-Notification-To:, ki je zahteva za prejem e-poštnega obvestila, "
"ko bo vaše sporočilo preneseno in prebrano s strani prejemnika. To funkcijo "
"mora podpirati in omogočiti prejemnikov e-poštni odjemalec; sicer ne bo "
"delovalo."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1738
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See <xref linkend=\"configure-security-reading-mdns\"/> for background "
"information and several ways to customize the read receipts that &kmail; "
"itself sends in response to a received Disposition-Notification-To: header "
"line."
msgstr ""
"Glejte <xref linkend=\"configure-security-reading-mdns\"/> za osnovne "
"informacije in več načinov za prilagajanje potrdil o branju, ki jih &kmail; "
"sam pošlje kot odgovor na prejeto naslovno vrstico Razpolaganje-obvestilo-"
"za:."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1745
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Options</guimenu><guimenuitem>Request Delivery Confirmation</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zahtevaj potrditev dostave</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1747
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you choose this option, &kmail; will insert a Return-Receipt-To: header "
"line in the message, which is a request to receive an email notification "
"once your message has been uploaded by your email server and delivered to "
"the recipient. This function must be supported by your outgoing email "
"server; otherwise, it will not work."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete to možnost, &kmail; bo v sporočilo vstavil naslovno vrstico Vrni-"
"Račun-Za:, ki je zahteva za prejem e-poštnega obvestila, ko bo vaš e-poštni "
"strežnik naložil vaše sporočilo in ga dostavil prejemniku. To funkcijo mora "
"podpirati vaš strežnik odhodne e-pošte; sicer ne bo delovalo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1756
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Options</guimenu><guisubmenu>Sign Message</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guisubmenu>Podpiši sporočilo</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1757
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Digitally signs the message using <application>OpenPGP</application> or an "
"X.509 certificate. You can learn more about this option in the <link linkend="
"\"pgp\">chapter on OpenPGP</link>."
msgstr ""
"Sporočilo digitalno podpiše s pomočjo <application>OpenPGP</application> ali "
"potrdila X.509. Več o tej možnosti lahko izveste v <link linkend=\"pgp"
"\">poglavju o OpenPGP</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1762
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Options</guimenu><guisubmenu>Encrypt Message</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guisubmenu>Šifriraj sporočilo</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1763
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Encrypts the message using <application>OpenPGP</application> or an X.509 "
"certificate. You can learn more about encryption in the <link linkend=\"pgp"
"\">chapter on OpenPGP</link>."
msgstr ""
"Šifrira sporočilo s pomočjo <application>OpenPGP</application> ali potrdila "
"X.509. Več o šifriranju lahko izveste v <link linkend=\"pgp\">poglavju o "
"OpenPGP</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1768
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Options</guimenu><guisubmenu>Cryptographic Message Format &gt;</"
"guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guisubmenu>Oblika kriptografskega sporočila &gt;"
"</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1769
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lets you choose the cryptographic message format to use when digitally "
"signing and/or encrypting this message. Please see <link linkend="
"\"cryptographic-message-formats\">Cryptographic Message Formats</link> for "
"more information."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča izbiro kriptografskega zapisa sporočila, ki ga želite uporabiti pri "
"digitalnem podpisovanju in/ali šifriranju tega sporočila. Za več informacij "
"glejte <link linkend=\"cryptographic-message-formats\">Oblike kriptografskih "
"sporočil</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1776
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Options</guimenu><guisubmenu>Rich Text Editing</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guisubmenu>Urejanje obogatenega besedila</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1777
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enables Rich Text (&ie;, &HTML;) editing."
msgstr "Omogoča urejanje obogatenega besedila (&ie;, &HTML;)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1781
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Options</guimenu><guisubmenu>Encoding &gt;</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guisubmenu>Kodiranje &gt;</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1782
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the charset encoding of this message. The chosen encoding will be "
"identified by a header line in the outgoing message. You can use "
"<guilabel>Auto</guilabel> in almost every case; &kmail; will notify you if "
"you must select a different encoding manually."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi kodiranje nabora znakov za to sporočilo. Izbrano kodiranje bo "
"označeno z naslovno vrstico v odhodnem sporočilu. <guilabel >Samodejno</"
"guilabel > lahko uporabite skoraj v vseh primerih; &kmail; vas bo obvestil, "
"če morate ročno izbrati drugo kodiranje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1788
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Options</guimenu><guimenuitem>Wordwrap</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guimenuitem>Previjanje besed</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1789
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles the automatic wordwrap feature. You may wish to turn this off when "
"pasting long lines (&eg;, &URL;s) that should not be wrapped."
msgstr ""
"Preklopi funkcijo samodejnega prelivanja besed. To boste morda želeli "
"izklopiti, ko lepite dolge vrstice (&eg;, &URL;), ki jih ne bi smeli preliti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1794
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Options</guimenu><guimenuitem>Automatic Spellchecking</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guimenuitem>Samodejno preverjanje črkovanja</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1795
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggles automatic spellchecking on or off."
msgstr "Vklopi ali izklopi samodejno preverjanje črkovanja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1799
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Options</guimenu><guimenuitem>Create Follow Up Reminder...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guimenuitem>Ustvari nadaljnji opomnik ...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1800
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Initiates a dialog allowing you to add a \"To Do\" item to your calendar. "
"This item is grayed out if the <ulink url=\"help:/"
"akonadi_followupreminder_agent\">Followup Reminder Agent</ulink> plugin has "
"not been activated."
msgstr ""
"Odpre pogovorno okno, ki vam omogoča, da v svoj koledar dodate element "
"»Opravila«. Ta element je zatemnjen, če vtičnik <ulink url=\"help:/"
"akonadi_followupreminder_agent\">Agent za nadaljnje opomnike</ulink> ni "
"aktiviran."

#. Tag: title
#: menus.docbook:1812
#, no-c-format
msgid "Attach Menu"
msgstr "Meni za prilaganje"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: menus.docbook:1814
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The Attach Menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Meni za prilaganje</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: menus.docbook:1820
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The Attach Menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Meni za prilaganje</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1823
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>The Attach Menu</para>"
msgstr "<para>Meni za prilaganje</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1829
#, no-c-format
msgid "This menu lets you select attachment options."
msgstr "Ta meni ti omogoča izbiro možnosti za priponke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1834
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Attach</guimenu><guimenuitem>Append Signature</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pripni</guimenu><guimenuitem>Dodaj podpis</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1835
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Appends your signature (<quote>footer</quote>) to the end of the message. "
"Please see <link linkend=\"configure-identity-signature\">Configure Identity "
"Signature</link> for details on configuring your signature."
msgstr ""
"Doda vaš podpis (<quote>noga</quote>) na konec sporočila. Prosimo, glejte "
"<link linkend=\"configure-identity-signature\">Konfiguracija podpisa "
"identitete</link> za podrobnosti o konfiguraciji vašega podpisa."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1841
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Attach</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prepend Signature</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pripni</guimenu><guimenuitem>Dodaj podpis</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1842
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Prepends your signature (<quote>header</quote>) at the beginning of the "
"message."
msgstr "Doda vaš podpis (<quote>glava</quote>) na začetek sporočila."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1846
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Attach</guimenu><guimenuitem>Insert Signature At Cursor Position</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Priloži</guimenu><guimenuitem>Vstavi podpis na položaj kazalca</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1848
#, no-c-format
msgid "Inserts your signature at the current cursor location."
msgstr "Vstavi vaš podpis na trenutno lokacijo kazalke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1852
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Attach</guimenu><guimenuitem>Attach Public Key...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Priloži</guimenu><guimenuitem>Priloži javni ključ ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1853
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the <guilabel>Attach Public OpenPGP Key</guilabel> dialog. Please see "
"<link linkend=\"configure-identity-cryptography-openpgp-sign\">Configure "
"Identity Cryptography OpenPGP Signing</link> for details."
msgstr ""
"Odpre pogovorno okno <guilabel>Priloži javni ključ OpenPGP</guilabel>. Za "
"podrobnosti si oglejte <link linkend=\"configure-identity-cryptography-"
"openpgp-sign\">Konfigurirajte podpisovanje OpenPGP kriptografije identitete</"
"link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1859
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Attach</guimenu><guimenuitem>Attach My Public Key</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Priloži</guimenu><guimenuitem>Priloži moj javni ključ</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1860
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Attaches your <application>GnuPG</application> public key, or your X.509 "
"certificate, (&ie;, the public key associated with your current identity) to "
"your message."
msgstr ""
"Vašemu sporočilu priloži vaš javni ključ <application>GnuPG</application> "
"ali vaše potrdilo X.509 (&ie; javni ključ, povezan z vašo trenutno "
"identiteto)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1866
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Attach</guimenu><guisubmenu>Attach &gt;</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Attach File...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Priloži</guimenu><guisubmenu>Priloži &gt;</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Priloži datoteko ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1868
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Attaches one or more files to the current message. Attachments are encrypted "
"by default (if the message is encrypted). Please see <link linkend="
"\"cryptographic-message-formats\">Cryptographic Message Formats</link> for "
"more information on encryption and attachments."
msgstr ""
"Priloži eno ali več datotek trenutnemu sporočilu. Priloge so privzeto "
"šifrirane (če je sporočilo šifrirano). Za več informacij o šifriranju in "
"prilogah glejte <link linkend=\"cryptographic-message-formats"
"\">Kriptografski formati sporočil</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1874
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Attach</guimenu><guisubmenu>Attach &gt;</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Attach Directory...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Priloži</guimenu><guisubmenu>Priloži &gt;</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Priloži imenik ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1876
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Creates a ZIP archive containing the selected Directory, and attaches the "
"archive to this message."
msgstr ""
"Ustvari arhiv ZIP, ki vsebuje izbrani imenik, in priloži arhiv temu "
"sporočilu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1881
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Attach</guimenu><guisubmenu>Attach &gt;</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Attach Own vCard</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Priloži</guimenu><guisubmenu>Priloži &gt;</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Priloži lastno vCard</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1883
#, no-c-format
msgid "Attaches your vCard to the current message."
msgstr "Priloži vašo vCard trenutnemu sporočilu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1887
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Attach</guimenu><guisubmenu>Attach &gt;</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Attach vCards...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Priloži</guimenu><guisubmenu>Priloži &gt;</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Priloži vCards ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1889
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a dialog with &kaddressbook; that lets you select one or more people "
"(&Ctrl; and left-click), and then attaches vCards for all those selected."
msgstr ""
"Odpre pogovorno okno z &kaddressbook; ki vam omogoča, da izberete eno ali "
"več oseb (&Ctrl; in levi klik), nato pa pripnete vCards za vse izbrane."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1894
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Attach</guimenu><guisubmenu>Attach &gt;</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Attach Text From Clipboard...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Priloži</guimenu><guisubmenu>Priloži &gt;</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Priloži besedilo iz odložišča ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1896
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the topmost item saved on the clipboard contains at least two bytes, a "
"file name dialog will open. &kmail; will create an attachment containing the "
"text from the clipboard, and give the attachment the name you have chosen."
msgstr ""
"Če najvišji element, shranjen v odložišče, vsebuje vsaj dva bajta, se odpre "
"pogovorno okno z imenom datoteke. &kmail; bo ustvaril priponko z besedilom "
"iz odložišča in priponki dal ime, ki ste ga izbrali."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1903
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Attach</guimenu><guimenuitem>Remove Attachment</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Priloži</guimenu><guimenuitem>Odstrani prilogo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1904
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Removes the selected attachment (selected via the attachment area beneath "
"the main composer window)."
msgstr ""
"Odstrani izbrano prilogo (izbrano v območju za priloge pod glavnim oknom "
"skladatelja)."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1906
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu item, and the next two, will be grayed out until an attachment is "
"selected."
msgstr ""
"Ta element menija in naslednja dva bosta zatemnjena, dokler ne izberete "
"priloge."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1911
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Attach</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save Attachment As...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Priloži</guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani prilogo kot ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1912
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saves the attachment selected in the attachment window as a file."
msgstr "Shrani prilogo, izbrano v oknu priloge, kot datoteko."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1916
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Attach</guimenu><guimenuitem>Attachment Properties</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Priloži</guimenu><guimenuitem>Lastnosti priloge</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1917
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays the <link linkend=\"attachments\">properties of the attachment</"
"link> that has been selected via the attachment window. It also lets you "
"sign/encrypt the attachment, and alter some of its other properties (name, "
"description, &MIME; type, &etc;)."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže <link linkend=\"attachments\">lastnosti priloge</link>, ki je bila "
"izbrana v oknu za priloge. Omogoča tudi podpisovanje/šifriranje priloge in "
"spreminjanje nekaterih njenih drugih lastnosti (ime, opis, vrsta &MIME; "
"&etc;)."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1945
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the menu item you are looking for is missing, please see <ulink url="
"\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-tools\">Tools Menu</ulink> of the "
"&kde; Fundamentals. The items listed here are &kmail; specific."
msgstr ""
"Če element menija, ki ga iščete, manjka, glejte <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/menus.html#menus-tools\">meni Orodja</ulink> v &kde; Osnove. "
"Tukaj navedeni elementi so &kmail; specifična."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1950
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Select Recipients...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izberi prejemnike ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1951
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a <guilabel>Select Recipient</guilabel> dialog, with the contents of "
"all your address books to select from."
msgstr ""
"Odpre pogovorno okno <guilabel>Izberi prejemnika</guilabel> z vsebino vseh "
"vaših imenikov, med katerimi lahko izbirate."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1956
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Addressbook...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Imenik ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1957
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Launches the <ulink url=\"help:/kaddressbook\">&kaddressbook;</ulink> "
"program."
msgstr ""
"Zažene program <ulink url=\"help:/kaddressbook\">&kaddressbook;</ulink>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1961
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save Distribution List...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani distribucijski seznam ...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1962
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a dialog that lets you save groups of contacts as a single named item. "
"Very handy if you frequently send the same message to all the members of a "
"club, for instance."
msgstr ""
"Odpre pogovorno okno, v katerem lahko shranite skupine stikov kot en "
"poimenovan element. Zelo priročno, če na primer pogosto pošiljate isto "
"sporočilo vsem članom kluba."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1967
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Autocorrect Text &gt;</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Samodejno popravi besedilo &gt;</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1968
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Performs autocorrection. You have two options: scan and autocorrect the "
"selected text, or apply <link linkend=\"configure-composer-autocorrection"
"\">autocorrection</link> to the whole message. This menu item will not be "
"present unless the <guilabel>Autocorrection</guilabel> plugin has been "
"loaded, and it won't work unless the Autocorrection function has been "
"enabled on the Composer configuration page."
msgstr ""
"Izvaja samodejno popravljanje. Imate dve možnosti: skenirajte in samodejno "
"popravite izbrano besedilo ali pa uporabite <link linkend=\"configure-"
"composer-autocorrection\">samodejni popravek</link> za celotno sporočilo. Ta "
"menijska postavka ne bo prisotna, razen če je bil naložen vtičnik "
"<guilabel>Samodejni popravek</guilabel>, in ne bo deloval, razen če je na "
"konfiguracijski strani Skladatelja omogočena funkcija Samodejni popravek."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1976
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Translator</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>T</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prevajalnik</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1978
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the <link linkend=\"using-the-translator\">translator window</link>."
msgstr "Odpre <link linkend=\"using-the-translator\">okno prevajalnika</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:1982
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Check Grammar (Language Tool)</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Preveri slovnico (orodje za jezik)</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:1983
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the grammar check window and examines your message, highlighting any "
"errors that are found. This feature does not continuously update the scanned "
"text as you type; you should first compose your message, then invoke grammar "
"check. This tool is not available unless the <guilabel>Grammar Check</"
"guilabel> plugin has been activated. Like the Translator function, Grammar "
"Check passes your message through a server (default server: https://"
"languagetool.org/api/v2) on the internet."
msgstr ""
"Odpre okno za preverjanje slovnice in pregleda vaše sporočilo ter označi vse "
"najdene napake. Ta funkcija med tipkanjem ne posodablja skeniranega "
"besedila; najprej sestavite svoje sporočilo, nato pokličite slovnično "
"preverjanje. To orodje ni na voljo, če ni aktiviran vtičnik "
"<guilabel>Preverjanje slovnice</guilabel>. Tako kot funkcija prevajalnika "
"tudi Grammar Check vaše sporočilo posreduje prek strežnika (privzeti "
"strežnik: https://languagetool.org/api/v2) v internetu."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:2013
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the menu item you seek is missing, please see <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">Settings Menu</ulink> of the &kde; "
"Fundamentals. The items listed here are &kmail; specific."
msgstr ""
"Če element menija, ki ga iščete, manjka, glejte <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">Meni z nastavitvami</ulink> v &kde; "
"Osnove. Tukaj navedeni elementi so &kmail; specifična."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:2018
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Toolbars Shown &gt;</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prikazane orodne vrstice &gt;</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:2019
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lets you control which toolbars are displayed. You may choose any "
"combination of three options: Main Toolbar (<guilabel>Send</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Queue</guilabel>, <guilabel>Rich Text</guilabel>, &etc;), HTML "
"Toolbar (<guilabel>Style</guilabel>, <guilabel>Font / Size</guilabel>, "
"&etc;), and Text Direction (in case you use a right-to-left script). Note "
"that the HTML Toolbar is easily toggled on and off via the <guibutton>Rich "
"Text</guibutton> button on the Main Toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča nadzor nad tem, katere orodne vrstice so prikazane. Izberete lahko "
"katero koli kombinacijo treh možnosti: Glavna orodna vrstica "
"(<guilabel>Pošlji</guilabel>, <guilabel>Čakalna vrsta</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Obogateno besedilo</guilabel> itd.), Orodna vrstica HTML "
"(<guilabel> Slog</guilabel>, <guilabel>Pisava/Velikost</guilabel> &etc;) in "
"Smer besedila (v primeru, da uporabljate skript od desne proti levi). "
"Upoštevajte, da je orodno vrstico HTML preprosto vklopiti in izklopiti z "
"gumbom <guibutton>Obogateno besedilo</guibutton> v glavni orodni vrstici."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menus.docbook:2027
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Spellchecker...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Črkovalnik ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:2028
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to configure <ulink url=\"help:/sonnet/\">&sonnet;</ulink>, "
"&kde;'s spell checker."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča vam konfiguracijo <ulink url=\"help:/sonnet/\">&sonnet;</ulink>, "
"črkovalnika &kde;."

#. Tag: para
#: menus.docbook:2053
